252
00:10:58.875 --> 00:11:00.583
To love is to trust!

253
00:11:00.667 --> 00:11:03.750
Today is a day to celebrate.
to have fun. to play.

254
00:11:03.833 --> 00:11:05.309
If you're not happy.
then let's call it a night.

255
00:11:05.333 --> 00:11:08.667
Fine! You should just go
and find some other woman

256
00:11:08.750 --> 00:11:11.500
who's younger than me.
can nurture your emotions.

257
00:11:11.583 --> 00:11:13.542
and support you. Tran Ngoc Son!

258
00:11:13.625 --> 00:11:16.083
Make a decision! Just one of the two!

259
00:11:16.167 --> 00:11:17.833
If you stay. then stop complaining.

260
00:11:17.917 --> 00:11:19.792
Or break up and set each other free.

261
00:11:19.875 --> 00:11:22.042
Easier said than done.

262
00:11:22.125 --> 00:11:24.518
There is nothing in the world
that you want that you can't get.

263
00:11:24.542 --> 00:11:26.625
- You crazy woman!
- <i>Be tough!</i>

264
00:11:26.708 --> 00:11:28.875
<i>Go full blast! Show me what you can do!</i>

265
00:11:28.958 --> 00:11:29.792
Who are you calling crazy?

266
00:11:29.875 --> 00:11:31.375
- Come on!
- Hey!

267
00:11:32.708 --> 00:11:34.292
<i>There! That's it!</i>

268
00:11:35.292 --> 00:11:36.958
What the hell. Ian?

269
00:11:37.458 --> 00:11:40.292
<i>If love doesn't work anymore.
then break up. set yourself free.</i>

270
00:11:40.375 --> 00:11:42.000
<i>Sometimes that's good for both of you.</i>

271
00:11:42.708 --> 00:11:44.059
<i>Thank you. everyone. for listening.</i>

272
00:11:44.083 --> 00:11:46.208
See you again next time!

273
00:11:54.750 --> 00:12:01.167
ONE WEEK LATER

274
00:12:01.792 --> 00:12:03.833
- Hello. Ms. Linh!
- Hello!

275
00:12:05.083 --> 00:12:06.667
- You guys had lunch?
- We did.

276
00:12:15.958 --> 00:12:17.167
- Food's ready?
- All done.

277
00:12:17.250 --> 00:12:18.250
- That's for Linh?
- Yep.

278
00:12:18.292 --> 00:12:19.292
So cute!

279
00:12:20.292 --> 00:12:22.167
- Hey. it smells good!
- Of course. I made it!

280
00:12:27.125 --> 00:12:29.167
<i>Just another peaceful day.</i>

281
00:12:29.250 --> 00:12:32.542
<i>Every day. I spend
30 minutes to slow down.</i>

282
00:12:32.625 --> 00:12:35.375
<i>to think about gains and losses.
to know how to love more</i>

283
00:12:35.458 --> 00:12:37.542
<i>with my husband. friends. and family.</i>

284
00:12:37.625 --> 00:12:41.292
<i>If you love me. you can follow
Hai Ian with a blue tick</i>

285
00:12:41.375 --> 00:12:42.542
<i>to spread this love.</i>

286
00:12:42.625 --> 00:12:44.542
Damn. she's funny!

287
00:12:46.333 --> 00:12:49.875
Hello. my golden girl!

288
00:12:49.958 --> 00:12:52.875
My sister! Hey. he brought you food.

289
00:12:52.958 --> 00:12:54.333
- Who?
- Your husband. of course.

290
00:12:54.417 --> 00:12:56.917
- Aw. thank you.
- Oh my God. Hai Linh!

291
00:12:57.000 --> 00:12:58.917
<i>Shoulder Sister</i> is now

292
00:12:59.000 --> 00:13:00.833
one of the top trending shows!

293
00:13:00.917 --> 00:13:03.625
Ads are pouring in
like men falling for me!

294
00:13:03.708 --> 00:13:05.583
- That's amazing!
- Ms. Linh!

295
00:13:05.667 --> 00:13:08.083
The vlog was filmed as a joke.
but it really worked.

296
00:13:08.167 --> 00:13:09.309
You didn't even show Phong's face.

297
00:13:09.333 --> 00:13:10.917
just his voice.

298
00:13:11.000 --> 00:13:13.417
- and the audience fell for you guys.
- So in love!

299
00:13:13.500 --> 00:13:16.042
Fans are now crazy for you guys!

300
00:13:16.125 --> 00:13:18.458
Hariwon and Tran Thanh
is no match for you guys!

301
00:13:18.542 --> 00:13:19.667
- Really?
- There's no way!

302
00:13:19.750 --> 00:13:24.208
Gosh. the audience and lights are ready
and you're still here chatting away.

303
00:13:24.792 --> 00:13:27.292
- Do you want to eat with me?
- Nope. you enjoy it.

304
00:13:28.083 --> 00:13:30.583
Work on keeping that gorgeous image
for my ads. Got it. cutie?

305
00:13:30.667 --> 00:13:34.167
Once we start cashing in.
I'll be your manager forever.

306
00:13:34.250 --> 00:13:36.625
- I know. I know!
- I've been counting money nonstop.

307
00:13:36.708 --> 00:13:38.042
I lick my fingers to count them.

308
00:13:38.125 --> 00:13:40.500
and nine out of ten are wrinkled
from the moisture.

309
00:13:40.583 --> 00:13:41.875
Now I have to wear gloves. see?

310
00:13:41.958 --> 00:13:43.292
Keep going. okay?

311
00:13:43.375 --> 00:13:44.833
This lady!

312
00:13:49.125 --> 00:13:50.875
Hello. baby!

313
00:13:50.958 --> 00:13:51.958
<i>Hello. sweetie!</i>

314
00:13:52.042 --> 00:13:54.458
<i>How did you get food to come
just in time for my hunger?</i>

315
00:13:55.625 --> 00:13:57.292
Because I'm your husband!

316
00:13:57.375 --> 00:13:59.125
Husband. where are you?

317
00:13:59.208 --> 00:14:01.667
She calls her husband
just like hollering at her child.

318
00:14:01.750 --> 00:14:03.500
They just got back from shopping.

319
00:14:04.583 --> 00:14:05.875
Welcome home!

320
00:14:05.958 --> 00:14:07.333
<i>Is our house almost ready?</i>

321
00:14:07.417 --> 00:14:08.417
I'm exhausted.

322
00:14:08.500 --> 00:14:10.167
<i>It's so noisy every day.</i>

323
00:14:10.250 --> 00:14:12.667
Hang on a little longer.
Our house is almost finished.

324
00:14:12.750 --> 00:14:14.583
Phong and I made
the best Quang noodles today!

325
00:14:14.667 --> 00:14:16.625
Wait. our ritual!

326
00:14:17.292 --> 00:14:18.458
Ah. understood.

327
00:14:18.542 --> 00:14:20.250
Ew. so in love.

328
00:14:20.333 --> 00:14:21.726
Like the fight never ever happened.

329
00:14:21.750 --> 00:14:23.071
Don't worry. The fight is coming.

330
00:14:23.125 --> 00:14:24.583
- Oh my God!
- What is this?

331
00:14:24.667 --> 00:14:25.750
- I told you so.
- What now?

332
00:14:25.833 --> 00:14:28.792
What's this lipstick stain?
Ben! Who visited today?

333
00:14:28.875 --> 00:14:30.500
Ah. I was coloring with her.

334
00:14:30.583 --> 00:14:32.143
That's not paint. it's a lipstick stain!

335
00:14:32.167 --> 00:14:33.417
It's paint. not lipstick!

336
00:14:33.500 --> 00:14:35.500
- You guys are colluding. aren't you?
- Oh my God!

337
00:14:35.583 --> 00:14:36.792
- I'll show you later.
- Stop it!

338
00:14:36.875 --> 00:14:38.667
No one kissed his neck.

339
00:14:38.750 --> 00:14:40.601
- I'm so hungry after eating.
- So hungry. my sugar is low.

340
00:14:40.625 --> 00:14:42.958
Luckily you're nothing like Son.

341
00:14:43.042 --> 00:14:44.458
- Useless.
- <i>Don't say that.</i>

342
00:14:45.083 --> 00:14:47.123
We can't shit-talk them
when we're living with them.

343
00:14:47.167 --> 00:14:49.250
- Then I'll continue after we moved.
- <i>Eat your food.</i>

344
00:14:49.333 --> 00:14:50.333
Then get back to work.

345
00:14:50.417 --> 00:14:51.583
Talk to you later.

346
00:14:54.125 --> 00:14:56.750
Everyone. settle down. Hai Linh is here.

347
00:14:56.833 --> 00:14:59.042
Ladies. get excited!

348
00:15:00.208 --> 00:15:01.542
My sister!

349
00:15:01.625 --> 00:15:04.917
- Oh my God. don't just sit there!
- Clap your hands. guys!

350
00:15:06.667 --> 00:15:09.583
Oh my God. you two.
hurry up and fix her hair.

351
00:15:09.667 --> 00:15:11.458
Hurry up!

352
00:15:11.542 --> 00:15:14.042
- What is it today. Tien?
- Today it's a rabbit.

353
00:15:14.125 --> 00:15:16.500
The story is amazing.
so I moved it up on the schedule.

354
00:15:16.583 --> 00:15:19.542
- Push it in when the brands are here.
- Smart!

355
00:15:19.625 --> 00:15:22.625
- Okay. get ready. Time is money.
- Okay then!

356
00:15:23.250 --> 00:15:24.375
Roll cameras.

357
00:15:24.458 --> 00:15:27.292
Three. two. one. action!

358
00:15:27.375 --> 00:15:32.500
Welcome back to <i>Shoulder Sister.</i>
ladies and gentlemen!

359
00:15:33.083 --> 00:15:35.375
- Looking fresh today!
- Of course. she's my talent.

360
00:15:35.458 --> 00:15:38.208
Today we will welcome
a very special guest.

361
00:15:38.792 --> 00:15:41.208
She wants to cover her face
and distort her voice.

362
00:15:41.292 --> 00:15:43.958
<i>Shoulder Sister</i> always
meets all guests' requests.

363
00:15:44.042 --> 00:15:47.750
And our character today
will transform into a very cute animal.

364
00:15:47.833 --> 00:15:50.500
Please welcome Rabbit!

365
00:16:02.167 --> 00:16:03.500
Why don't you introduce yourself?

366
00:16:07.083 --> 00:16:08.292
Rabbit?

367
00:16:09.042 --> 00:16:10.042
Rabbit!

368
00:16:10.625 --> 00:16:11.792
Why isn't she answering?

369
00:16:11.875 --> 00:16:14.125
- Be patient. sister. be patient.
- Rabbit!

370
00:16:14.875 --> 00:16:16.708
- Yes?
- Who are you?

371
00:16:16.792 --> 00:16:18.875
Introduce yourself to everyone.

372
00:16:22.042 --> 00:16:23.125
I'm Bunnie.

373
00:16:23.708 --> 00:16:26.333
Oh my God. obviously you're Rabbit.
She was asking for a name.

374
00:16:26.417 --> 00:16:27.833
Oh my God!

375
00:16:28.667 --> 00:16:31.375
Um. okay. everyone here
can see that you're Rabbit.

376
00:16:31.458 --> 00:16:33.542
I mean. let's talk more about you.

377
00:16:33.625 --> 00:16:35.875
Where are you from? What is your job?

378
00:16:36.583 --> 00:16:38.417
My nickname is Bunnie.

379
00:16:38.500 --> 00:16:40.125
- Oh really?
- My…

380
00:16:40.792 --> 00:16:41.917
Real name is Nhat Ha.

381
00:16:43.917 --> 00:16:46.625
- Okay. she's warming up.
- I work in an office.

382
00:16:48.375 --> 00:16:50.500
So. what can I do for you today?

383
00:17:00.125 --> 00:17:01.292
Bunnie!

384
00:17:01.375 --> 00:17:03.000
Oh my gosh!

385
00:17:03.083 --> 00:17:05.750
- There are three sponsors sitting here.
- Are you ready to share?

386
00:17:05.833 --> 00:17:07.601
Trust me. her story is great.
Got goosebumps interviewing…

387
00:17:07.625 --> 00:17:09.667
You call that a great story?

388
00:17:09.750 --> 00:17:11.458
Bunnie.

389
00:17:11.542 --> 00:17:13.622
- I'll scratch your face if it's not good.
- It's okay.

390
00:17:14.042 --> 00:17:15.875
Take a deep breath. Calm down.

391
00:17:15.958 --> 00:17:18.208
Make yourself at home.

392
00:17:20.125 --> 00:17:21.208
Sister…

393
00:17:21.292 --> 00:17:22.625
Oh. I'm here.

394
00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:27.125
Can you show me how to break up?

395
00:17:33.458 --> 00:17:36.659
You mean… She's here because she doesn't
know how to break up with her boyfriend?

396
00:17:37.500 --> 00:17:39.458
You really mean this?

397
00:17:44.125 --> 00:17:45.708
Let's get started.

398
00:17:55.042 --> 00:17:59.542
BUNNIE

399
00:18:11.042 --> 00:18:13.292
- Still kissing?
- It's nothing. Are you guys jealous?

400
00:18:13.375 --> 00:18:15.875
Let them be.
They won't last even five minutes.

401
00:18:15.958 --> 00:18:17.083
Hey. Linh's home.

402
00:18:17.167 --> 00:18:18.250
- Hello. everyone.
- Sweetie!

403
00:18:18.333 --> 00:18:19.250
That's so fun.

404
00:18:19.333 --> 00:18:20.625
Come hang out for a bit.

405
00:18:20.708 --> 00:18:23.208
It's okay. you guys go ahead.
I'm a bit tired.

406
00:18:23.292 --> 00:18:25.167
Hey. you two. there's a kid here.

407
00:18:25.250 --> 00:18:27.417
- They've been kissing for ages.
- Have fun. everyone.

408
00:18:27.500 --> 00:18:30.292
She's dry like a stone.
She doesn't like karaoke.

409
00:18:30.375 --> 00:18:32.167
She never liked family activities.

410
00:18:32.250 --> 00:18:34.208
Sometimes I feel like
she's looking down on us.

411
00:18:34.292 --> 00:18:35.458
Oh. maybe that's true.

412
00:19:02.292 --> 00:19:03.500
Hello. aunties.

413
00:19:37.542 --> 00:19:38.625
Why are you here?

414
00:19:39.125 --> 00:19:42.083
You're refusing to see me.
so I had to find a way.

415
00:19:43.958 --> 00:19:46.625
You can't just break my lock like that.

416
00:19:47.792 --> 00:19:49.417
<i>I'm hiding from my boyfriend.</i>

417
00:19:50.250 --> 00:19:52.458
He doesn't trust me.

418
00:19:52.542 --> 00:19:54.083
Are you okay?

419
00:19:54.667 --> 00:19:57.167
Does he… abuse you in any way?

420
00:19:57.250 --> 00:19:58.792
Where were you?

421
00:20:01.000 --> 00:20:02.240
Wherever I went is my business.

422
00:20:03.000 --> 00:20:05.167
It's Sunday. You didn't have to work.

423
00:20:06.000 --> 00:20:07.417
Where did you go?

424
00:20:08.333 --> 00:20:11.333
Okay. now I need to know.
What exactly did he do to you?

425
00:20:13.167 --> 00:20:15.833
- He stalked me…
- Why are you so dressed up?

426
00:20:15.917 --> 00:20:17.458
<i>Controlled me…</i>

427
00:20:17.542 --> 00:20:18.708
Were you out with him?

428
00:20:18.792 --> 00:20:20.333
I wasn't out with anyone.

429
00:20:20.417 --> 00:20:21.958
Why are you dressed up then?

430
00:20:22.042 --> 00:20:24.875
I said it's my right to go where I want.
It's none of your business.

431
00:20:24.958 --> 00:20:26.625
Manipulated me…

432
00:20:30.833 --> 00:20:33.500
You haven't picked up my calls for days.

433
00:20:33.583 --> 00:20:35.167
You didn't even reply to my texts.

434
00:20:35.833 --> 00:20:37.167
You're hiding from me.

435
00:20:37.250 --> 00:20:39.309
Now that I'm here.
you say to stay out of your business.

436
00:20:39.333 --> 00:20:41.167
What then? What do you want?

437
00:20:42.417 --> 00:20:44.917
- I'm not hiding.
- Did I do something wrong?

438
00:20:45.000 --> 00:20:47.750
If I did. tell me. so I can change.
Why are you running from me?

439
00:20:47.833 --> 00:20:49.750
I have no idea what I did wrong to you.

440
00:20:49.833 --> 00:20:51.792
Now you're telling me
not to worry about you.

441
00:20:51.875 --> 00:20:53.042
What do you mean. Bunnie?

442
00:20:53.125 --> 00:20:54.708
You said we'd give each other time.

443
00:20:54.792 --> 00:20:57.208
I gave you time. I didn't bother you.

444
00:20:57.292 --> 00:20:59.252
I disappeared. but you have
to answer me at least.

445
00:20:59.333 --> 00:21:02.375
You didn't even contact me. You...
What the heck?

446
00:21:02.458 --> 00:21:03.625
Kim…

447
00:21:03.708 --> 00:21:05.292
Sit down first.

448
00:21:05.375 --> 00:21:09.500
You have to calm down
so I can talk to you. Have a seat.

449
00:21:09.583 --> 00:21:11.750
You acting like this is scaring me.

450
00:21:11.833 --> 00:21:14.542
I'm your boyfriend.
Why would you be afraid of me?

451
00:21:14.625 --> 00:21:15.667
<i>Tormented me…</i>

452
00:21:15.750 --> 00:21:19.208
What did I do that scared you?
Tell me? I'm your boyfriend.

453
00:21:19.292 --> 00:21:20.667
Why are you scared of me?

454
00:21:20.750 --> 00:21:22.208
I'm not scared of you.

455
00:21:22.292 --> 00:21:25.167
What I'm scared of
is us meeting like this every time.

456
00:21:25.250 --> 00:21:28.458
I told you to give me time.
I need to rest.

457
00:21:28.542 --> 00:21:30.309
but now you're like this.
and I'm so stressed out.

458
00:21:30.333 --> 00:21:32.250
So you're stressed. and I'm not?

459
00:21:33.167 --> 00:21:34.667
Our problem has never been resolved.

460
00:21:34.750 --> 00:21:35.958
I told you to quit your job.

461
00:21:36.042 --> 00:21:38.750
Let me take care of you. I can do it.

462
00:21:38.833 --> 00:21:41.625
You don't trust me. you didn't quit.
now you're going out with him.

463
00:21:41.708 --> 00:21:43.375
and when I ask you.

464
00:21:43.458 --> 00:21:46.167
you say it's none of my business.
What the heck is that?

465
00:21:46.250 --> 00:21:47.375
What is it?

466
00:21:47.958 --> 00:21:49.833
Tell me what I have to do now.

467
00:21:58.333 --> 00:21:59.667
You love him. don't you?

468
00:22:00.875 --> 00:22:01.958
I don't.

469
00:22:04.250 --> 00:22:07.125
How many times do I have
to tell you that I don't love him?

470
00:22:08.625 --> 00:22:09.750
Him?

471
00:22:12.542 --> 00:22:13.833
What did you just say?

472
00:22:13.917 --> 00:22:15.125
Him?

473
00:22:16.792 --> 00:22:18.542
Fuck. "him"…

474
00:22:19.417 --> 00:22:20.708
Him?

475
00:22:22.542 --> 00:22:25.167
What did you just say?

476
00:22:25.750 --> 00:22:26.958
Him?

477
00:22:27.042 --> 00:22:29.375
The way you say it
makes me feel like you love him.

478
00:22:30.417 --> 00:22:32.375
<i>Let's look at it this way.</i>

479
00:22:33.583 --> 00:22:35.708
You're sitting on a train.

480
00:22:35.792 --> 00:22:38.125
You keep going. but never reach the end.

481
00:22:38.625 --> 00:22:40.083
Do you know why?

482
00:22:40.167 --> 00:22:43.958
Because you are sitting in the wrong car.
This car is not for you.

483
00:22:44.042 --> 00:22:47.000
<i>If you just sit there. it will
take you further and further away.</i>

484
00:22:47.083 --> 00:22:49.000
You fell for him. damn it…

485
00:22:49.083 --> 00:22:50.667
You don't love me anymore. do you?

486
00:22:50.750 --> 00:22:52.875
Or is it because I'm poor?

487
00:22:52.958 --> 00:22:56.500
Say something. dear?
Bunnie. you don't love me anymore?

488
00:22:57.708 --> 00:22:59.167
Bunnie!

489
00:22:59.250 --> 00:23:00.500
He never hit me. but…

490
00:23:00.583 --> 00:23:01.875
Bunnie!

491
00:23:01.958 --> 00:23:03.042
Answer me!

492
00:23:03.125 --> 00:23:04.458
Or is it because I'm incompetent…

493
00:23:05.875 --> 00:23:08.250
- Kim! Calm down!
- You love him. right? Huh?

494
00:23:08.333 --> 00:23:09.708
- Kim!
- You love him. don't you?

495
00:23:09.792 --> 00:23:11.000
- Kim!
- You love him!

496
00:23:11.083 --> 00:23:12.601
I think this is a form of mental abuse.

497
00:23:12.625 --> 00:23:15.208
- You can't live like that anymore.
<i>- Kim!</i>

498
00:23:15.292 --> 00:23:17.125
Kim! Oh God. you have to calm down… Kim!

499
00:23:17.208 --> 00:23:18.750
People always end up regretting.

500
00:23:18.833 --> 00:23:20.500
Regret the time in the past.

501
00:23:20.583 --> 00:23:22.667
Regret the effort
of sitting on that train.

502
00:23:23.250 --> 00:23:24.458
However.

503
00:23:24.542 --> 00:23:26.958
why be so hung up and get stuck for good?

504
00:23:27.042 --> 00:23:29.042
We've got the right
to take plenty of trains.

505
00:23:29.542 --> 00:23:30.583
Now listen to me.

506
00:23:31.417 --> 00:23:32.583
Get off.

507
00:23:33.083 --> 00:23:35.208
Take another train that suits you.

508
00:23:35.292 --> 00:23:36.708
Kim!

509
00:23:36.792 --> 00:23:38.958
Calm down and listen to me.

510
00:23:40.708 --> 00:23:42.958
Girls. don't torment yourself like that.

511
00:23:44.458 --> 00:23:46.292
I'm tired.

512
00:23:49.292 --> 00:23:51.000
Can we break up?

513
00:23:52.250 --> 00:23:54.226
I hate that sentence.
I don't want to hear that sentence.

514
00:23:54.250 --> 00:23:56.101
- You still love me. right?
- Kim. calm down. Calm down. Kim.

515
00:23:56.125 --> 00:23:58.083
- Kim. Kim. you have to…
- Still love me. right?

516
00:23:58.167 --> 00:23:59.559
- You still love me. right?
- Listen to me. listen to me…

517
00:23:59.583 --> 00:24:01.042
Kim. you have to calm down...

518
00:24:08.542 --> 00:24:09.917
It hurt so much…

519
00:24:10.000 --> 00:24:12.917
I'm sorry. I'm sorry. Sorry. sorry…

520
00:24:13.000 --> 00:24:14.292
Hold on a moment.

521
00:24:14.792 --> 00:24:15.833
Where's our povidin?

522
00:24:16.833 --> 00:24:17.917
Bunnie! Bunnie!

523
00:24:22.958 --> 00:24:24.000
Bunnie!

524
00:24:25.333 --> 00:24:26.667
<i>Bunnie!</i>

525
00:24:46.417 --> 00:24:48.458
<i>But he's not a bad person.</i>

526
00:24:49.708 --> 00:24:52.042
<i>It would've been better
if he was a bad person.</i>

527
00:24:53.333 --> 00:24:55.625
I tried very hard to make money.

528
00:24:55.708 --> 00:24:58.458
You can't expect me to do something
I'm not good at.

529
00:24:58.542 --> 00:25:00.292
Let's stop talking about money.

530
00:25:00.375 --> 00:25:02.375
I don't want to talk to you anymore.
I'm too tired.

531
00:25:07.833 --> 00:25:10.417
<i>For me. he tried hard
and sacrificed a lot.</i>

532
00:25:12.042 --> 00:25:13.208
<i>Actually…</i>

533
00:25:13.875 --> 00:25:17.958
He only torments me when he feels low.
but other than that…

534
00:25:20.292 --> 00:25:21.875
<i>He's really good to me.</i>

535
00:25:23.750 --> 00:25:25.500
<i>Where's my Bunnie?</i>

536
00:25:28.708 --> 00:25:31.583
- Food's here! Sorry…
- I'm starving.

537
00:25:31.667 --> 00:25:33.000
I told you I'd get it.

538
00:25:33.083 --> 00:25:34.559
- but you still went and bought it.
- I was worried you'd get tired.

539
00:25:34.583 --> 00:25:37.375
Quit your job. Don't do this.
There's no money here.

540
00:25:37.458 --> 00:25:39.875
Don't do it anymore. Let me work.
and I'll take care of you.

541
00:25:39.958 --> 00:25:42.250
It's okay. I'm not disabled.
What are you talking about?

542
00:25:42.333 --> 00:25:43.667
Come on…

543
00:25:45.458 --> 00:25:48.417
It's not easy to leave someone
who loves you.

544
00:26:02.292 --> 00:26:03.417
What the hell!

545
00:26:04.292 --> 00:26:05.292
Why are you so jumpy?

546
00:26:05.375 --> 00:26:08.083
Why do you keep doing silly stuff?

547
00:26:08.167 --> 00:26:09.476
Why won't you come hang out with us?

548
00:26:09.500 --> 00:26:10.583
I'm tired.

549
00:26:10.667 --> 00:26:12.333
Those ladies have so much free time.

550
00:26:12.417 --> 00:26:15.958
Doesn't work at all. just drinks. sings.
parties nonstop. way too loud!

551
00:26:16.042 --> 00:26:18.458
Come on. they work a lot.
They deserve to have some fun!

552
00:26:18.542 --> 00:26:21.417
Unlike you. always working non-stop
and refusing to enjoy anything.

553
00:26:21.500 --> 00:26:23.375
Hey. speaking of work.

554
00:26:23.458 --> 00:26:25.625
A guest on my show had such a sad story.

555
00:26:25.708 --> 00:26:27.500
She said she's being abused.

556
00:26:28.167 --> 00:26:31.792
Then she said something
that has been on my mind.

557
00:26:31.875 --> 00:26:33.125
What?

558
00:26:33.208 --> 00:26:36.708
It's hard to let go of someone
who loves you too much.

559
00:26:38.083 --> 00:26:40.583
Isn't it great?
It's worth thinking about. isn't it?

560
00:26:41.708 --> 00:26:44.042
Then I thought about Son and Ian.

561
00:26:44.583 --> 00:26:49.000
Ian must love Son a lot
to still be with him.

562
00:26:49.083 --> 00:26:53.417
What kind of man is that useless
and even ungrateful?

563
00:26:53.500 --> 00:26:54.667
Can't make any money.

564
00:26:54.750 --> 00:26:57.311
but he's really good at making her jealous
and getting yelled at.

565
00:26:57.375 --> 00:26:58.917
Now you can see

566
00:26:59.000 --> 00:27:01.250
there is no one
as perfect as your husband.

567
00:27:01.333 --> 00:27:02.208
What?

568
00:27:02.292 --> 00:27:03.972
- Are you saying you're perfect?
- Of course.

569
00:27:04.000 --> 00:27:05.167
Let me see!

570
00:27:07.792 --> 00:27:09.000
Other side.

571
00:27:11.417 --> 00:27:13.000
- You're fine.
- That's it?

572
00:27:14.125 --> 00:27:15.958
- Just fine?
- Yep!

573
00:27:18.292 --> 00:27:19.917
- Fine?
- Fine.

574
00:27:26.792 --> 00:27:28.333
Ha! How dare you?

575
00:27:29.167 --> 00:27:31.292
Linh! Phong!

576
00:27:31.375 --> 00:27:33.792
- Get down here. or I'll die!
- What is it?

577
00:27:33.875 --> 00:27:35.268
- Let them be.
- Ian is calling for us!

578
00:27:35.292 --> 00:27:36.375
Make the call!

579
00:27:37.375 --> 00:27:39.250
Pick up the phone and call her right away.

580
00:27:39.917 --> 00:27:42.042
See? Of course. he wouldn't call.

581
00:27:42.125 --> 00:27:44.250
He wouldn't dare let her answer the phone.

582
00:27:44.333 --> 00:27:45.875
Make the call. She's going crazy.

583
00:27:45.958 --> 00:27:48.083
- What's up?
- There you are. Linh. come here!

584
00:27:48.167 --> 00:27:49.851
You want fairness. right?
Let me talk to Linh.

585
00:27:49.875 --> 00:27:52.042
You went through his phone again.
didn't you?

586
00:27:52.125 --> 00:27:54.292
Your husband is an extremely kind
and decent guy.

587
00:27:54.375 --> 00:27:56.083
so you will never have to do this.

588
00:27:56.167 --> 00:27:57.750
My husband is an asshole.

589
00:27:57.833 --> 00:27:59.917
so if I didn't pick up his phone today.

590
00:28:00.000 --> 00:28:02.083
how would I know
there was a girl named +Th

591
00:28:02.167 --> 00:28:05.083
who texted. "I just broke up. Let's meet."

592
00:28:05.167 --> 00:28:06.917
She's my cousin from my hometown.

593
00:28:07.000 --> 00:28:08.542
What cousin do I not know?

594
00:28:08.625 --> 00:28:10.958
Just call her what she is.
your emotional support chick.

595
00:28:11.042 --> 00:28:12.250
I've said it a thousand times.

596
00:28:12.333 --> 00:28:16.708
Her name's Thu. from my hometown.
She broke up and wanted to vent to me.

597
00:28:16.792 --> 00:28:18.601
It's not a big deal.
Why drag it out like this?

598
00:28:18.625 --> 00:28:20.333
Why didn't you save her as "Thu" then?

599
00:28:20.417 --> 00:28:23.250
- What the hell is +Th?
- + is family.

600
00:28:23.333 --> 00:28:26.000
For example. Linh is +L. Phong is +Ph.

601
00:28:26.083 --> 00:28:29.208
Ah. Linh. come here. + is family.

602
00:28:29.292 --> 00:28:30.917
Do you know what I'm saved as?

603
00:28:31.000 --> 00:28:33.500
"Oldie". and no + sign.

604
00:28:33.583 --> 00:28:36.375
Just make the call. then.
She's your cousin. Why are you scared?

605
00:28:36.458 --> 00:28:38.792
It's not that I'm scared.
I just don't want to call.

606
00:28:39.375 --> 00:28:41.500
I don't want to call
and let my wife yell at her.

607
00:28:42.542 --> 00:28:44.542
You say it like I'm a psychopath?

608
00:28:44.625 --> 00:28:45.833
Have I ever yelled at anyone?

609
00:28:45.917 --> 00:28:48.875
A few days ago. you called and yelled
at Lee. his ex. Did you forget?

610
00:28:48.958 --> 00:28:51.838
She even yelled at the birthday girl.
even though she didn't do anything.

611
00:28:51.917 --> 00:28:53.833
Don't tattle on your friend!

612
00:28:53.917 --> 00:28:56.792
Those two ungrateful bitches
deserve to be scolded.

613
00:28:56.875 --> 00:28:58.000
Call her.

614
00:28:58.083 --> 00:29:00.125
I'm here. I won't let her yell at anyone.

615
00:29:00.208 --> 00:29:02.208
Why are we fussing
over a simple phone call?

616
00:29:02.292 --> 00:29:03.917
Call her if you have nothing to hide.

617
00:29:04.000 --> 00:29:09.792
CALLING +TH

618
00:29:15.792 --> 00:29:17.500
She wouldn't dare answer the phone.

619
00:29:18.167 --> 00:29:19.167
You're joking. right?

620
00:29:19.208 --> 00:29:20.849
She might be in the shower or the toilet.

621
00:29:20.875 --> 00:29:22.542
Why must she answer when you call?

622
00:29:22.625 --> 00:29:24.625
Maybe she'll pick up a call
from an unknown number.

623
00:29:25.708 --> 00:29:26.875
Should we call her?

624
00:29:26.958 --> 00:29:28.358
Ian. give me the number. I'll call.

625
00:29:29.000 --> 00:29:30.875
Let's just get this over with.

626
00:29:30.958 --> 00:29:32.375
Clarity is good.

627
00:29:32.458 --> 00:29:35.417
Give me that. You guys need
to stop bickering. It's exhausting.

628
00:29:50.917 --> 00:29:52.208
<i>Who's this?</i>

629
00:29:54.417 --> 00:29:55.417
<i>Hello?</i>

630
00:29:56.750 --> 00:29:58.000
<i>Hello. Who is it?</i>

631
00:29:59.917 --> 00:30:01.208
Say something.

632
00:30:03.208 --> 00:30:04.417
What do you have to say?

633
00:30:04.500 --> 00:30:06.125
She picked up. Say something.

634
00:30:06.208 --> 00:30:08.708
You're all colluding together.
What the hell is there to say?

635
00:30:08.792 --> 00:30:11.000
Why do I have to talk to a home wrecker?

636
00:30:12.583 --> 00:30:15.792
I didn't expect you
to treat me so horribly.

637
00:30:15.875 --> 00:30:17.250
Tran Ngoc Son.

638
00:30:18.458 --> 00:30:20.708
Go live with her.

639
00:30:20.792 --> 00:30:22.625
Get the hell out of my house.

640
00:30:29.292 --> 00:30:30.458
You said it yourself.

641
00:30:33.250 --> 00:30:34.417
Son…

642
00:30:36.167 --> 00:30:37.792
I knew it.

643
00:30:37.875 --> 00:30:39.667
He leaves as soon as I said so.

644
00:30:41.208 --> 00:30:44.542
I never thought my life
would be this miserable.

645
00:30:44.625 --> 00:30:46.292
I will divorce him today.

646
00:30:48.083 --> 00:30:49.243
Ian. maybe we should go home.

647
00:30:49.792 --> 00:30:51.434
There are too many people here.
He must be embarrassed.

648
00:30:51.458 --> 00:30:53.417
We'll give you guys some space to talk.

649
00:30:53.500 --> 00:30:55.292
He's a man. He has his ego.

650
00:30:55.375 --> 00:30:56.792
I'm speechless with you.

651
00:30:56.875 --> 00:30:58.500
There are too many people here.

652
00:30:58.583 --> 00:31:00.833
- We should head out.
- I'll die if you guys leave.

653
00:31:00.917 --> 00:31:01.792
What do you mean?

654
00:31:01.875 --> 00:31:03.375
I told you from the beginning.

655
00:31:03.458 --> 00:31:05.583
If you love him but can't trust him.
then break up.

656
00:31:05.667 --> 00:31:07.458
No one loves and suffers like you.

657
00:31:07.542 --> 00:31:10.250
You are my sister. You should love me.

658
00:31:10.333 --> 00:31:12.500
Why do you keep telling me
to break up. Linh?

659
00:31:12.583 --> 00:31:13.792
You talk a good talk.

660
00:31:13.875 --> 00:31:17.208
I'll wait and see. If it were you.
how would you handle it?

661
00:31:17.792 --> 00:31:19.667
He does nothing all day.

662
00:31:19.750 --> 00:31:21.333
<i>Just keep staring at the phone.</i>

663
00:31:21.417 --> 00:31:22.833
<i>His face is cunning.</i>

664
00:31:22.917 --> 00:31:24.875
<i>definitely texting some homewreckers.</i>

665
00:31:24.958 --> 00:31:27.226
<i>Says he'll watch the kid.
but ends up just playing video games.</i>

666
00:31:27.250 --> 00:31:29.000
<i>I take care of everything at the company.</i>

667
00:31:29.083 --> 00:31:31.708
If you don't work with Unios.
then who else will you work with?

668
00:31:31.792 --> 00:31:33.432
Our lighting tech is the best in Vietnam.

669
00:31:33.500 --> 00:31:35.768
Wouldn't it be good if he could
become a director like Phong?

670
00:31:35.792 --> 00:31:38.667
His only job is to pay the employees.

671
00:31:38.750 --> 00:31:40.458
He either underpays or overpays.

672
00:31:40.542 --> 00:31:42.583
Sometimes he even double pays.

673
00:31:42.667 --> 00:31:44.667
Cunning with a huge ego.

674
00:31:44.750 --> 00:31:47.292
Apart from me. he has no one.

675
00:31:47.875 --> 00:31:49.125
He doesn't have any friends.

676
00:31:49.208 --> 00:31:50.208
See?

677
00:31:50.542 --> 00:31:53.375
Where are you going?
You're leaving for real?

678
00:32:01.083 --> 00:32:03.042
If you leave now.

679
00:32:03.583 --> 00:32:05.167
don't ever come back.

680
00:32:05.250 --> 00:32:09.208
Let me see if that bitch +Th
can take care of you the way I do.

681
00:32:09.292 --> 00:32:10.875
And where's trash like you

682
00:32:10.958 --> 00:32:12.583
gonna get cash to live anyway?

683
00:32:19.333 --> 00:32:20.458
Ian…

684
00:32:21.000 --> 00:32:23.917
You are a woman
who doesn't know when to stop.

685
00:32:27.417 --> 00:32:28.833
I'm not taking anything from you.

686
00:32:33.125 --> 00:32:34.417
The suitcase is mine.

687
00:32:45.042 --> 00:32:46.833
Son! Son!

688
00:32:48.083 --> 00:32:49.500
I'll go after him.

689
00:32:50.000 --> 00:32:50.875
Your phone. Son.

690
00:32:50.958 --> 00:32:53.042
No need to follow him. Phong!

691
00:32:54.667 --> 00:32:55.833
Let him go!

692
00:32:55.917 --> 00:32:57.917
Ian. I'm begging you.

693
00:33:21.250 --> 00:33:27.792
ONE MONTH LATER

694
00:33:44.875 --> 00:33:46.042
Thank you.

695
00:34:13.333 --> 00:34:17.792
TRAN NGOC SON

696
00:34:26.833 --> 00:34:29.292
<i>Bunnie. I need you to get
straight to the point.</i>

697
00:34:30.167 --> 00:34:33.042
<i>I know you're troubled.</i>

698
00:34:33.125 --> 00:34:34.875
<i>but this is your second time here.</i>

699
00:34:34.958 --> 00:34:37.167
<i>yet your story is still very vague.</i>

700
00:34:38.167 --> 00:34:41.958
If you won't just say it straight out.
I really don't know how to help you.

701
00:34:42.042 --> 00:34:43.750
She is talking in circles. isn't she?

702
00:34:43.833 --> 00:34:45.458
But people like her story.

703
00:34:45.542 --> 00:34:46.667
Is that so?

704
00:34:46.750 --> 00:34:49.000
Can you be more specific?

705
00:34:50.458 --> 00:34:51.583
I…

706
00:34:57.375 --> 00:34:58.958
I'm dating a married man.

707
00:35:00.542 --> 00:35:01.875
OMG!

708
00:35:01.958 --> 00:35:03.042
That's wild!

709
00:35:03.125 --> 00:35:06.292
Views! Views are pouring in!

710
00:35:06.375 --> 00:35:09.083
I believe that everyone
has their reasons for doing anything.

711
00:35:09.167 --> 00:35:13.500
It can be wrong for everyone.
but maybe it's right for you. so what?

712
00:35:13.583 --> 00:35:15.083
So…

713
00:35:15.167 --> 00:35:16.708
I want to hear your reason.

714
00:35:17.792 --> 00:35:19.333
I know he's not happy.

715
00:35:19.958 --> 00:35:23.417
<i>And he's living with people
he doesn't love anymore.</i>

716
00:35:24.042 --> 00:35:25.792
He and his wife are separating.

717
00:35:26.458 --> 00:35:28.083
He told me to wait for him.

718
00:35:28.167 --> 00:35:29.167
You believe him?

719
00:35:29.208 --> 00:35:31.542
Oh. so his wife is messed up.

720
00:35:31.625 --> 00:35:33.708
and then when this girl showed up.
he fell for her.

721
00:35:33.792 --> 00:35:35.792
How long ago did you two start?

722
00:35:35.875 --> 00:35:36.958
One month.

723
00:35:39.458 --> 00:35:41.833
<i>I think he and I are quite similar.</i>

724
00:35:41.917 --> 00:35:45.875
<i>Both are in relationships
where they get tormented.</i>

725
00:35:46.458 --> 00:35:49.000
I don't know if you understand
how bad it feels

726
00:35:49.083 --> 00:35:52.667
to be with someone you can't love anymore.

727
00:35:52.750 --> 00:35:56.125
Sorry. may I ask for your age?

728
00:35:56.208 --> 00:35:57.417
I'm 28.

729
00:35:57.500 --> 00:35:58.958
Twenty-eight years old…

730
00:35:59.042 --> 00:36:00.792
You're still very young.

731
00:36:00.875 --> 00:36:02.917
There are plenty of fish in the sea.

732
00:36:03.000 --> 00:36:05.833
Why would you choose a fish
that is on someone else's plate?

733
00:36:05.917 --> 00:36:07.851
I think that feeling
is kind of like a turn on. right?

734
00:36:07.875 --> 00:36:10.708
- I see it a lot now.
- Yeah. maybe they like that.

735
00:36:10.792 --> 00:36:12.351
Actually. I'm doing what you told me to.

736
00:36:12.375 --> 00:36:14.000
What is it? What did she say?

737
00:36:14.083 --> 00:36:15.083
You said

738
00:36:15.167 --> 00:36:18.792
I was on a wrong train.
and I needed to get off.

739
00:36:19.583 --> 00:36:21.000
<i>I'm on a new train now.</i>

740
00:36:21.792 --> 00:36:24.500
<i>I feel that this new train
is meant for me.</i>

741
00:36:25.000 --> 00:36:26.958
I feel more appreciated.

742
00:36:27.042 --> 00:36:28.375
I'm more confident.

743
00:36:28.458 --> 00:36:32.417
I just don't know if this train
is really suitable for me or not because…

744
00:36:33.708 --> 00:36:35.542
I've always made the wrong choices.

745
00:36:35.625 --> 00:36:37.809
Well. obviously stealing
someone's husband is not right.

746
00:36:37.833 --> 00:36:38.833
But…

747
00:36:40.958 --> 00:36:43.208
Are you sure you're not wrong this time?

748
00:36:44.750 --> 00:36:46.583
I'm not sure I'm right.

749
00:36:49.125 --> 00:36:51.458
But in life. no one is always right.

750
00:36:51.542 --> 00:36:53.292
It's okay to be wrong.

751
00:36:53.792 --> 00:36:55.125
But I still want to try.

752
00:36:55.792 --> 00:36:59.875
Your advice gave me
the confidence to decide

753
00:37:00.750 --> 00:37:02.458
that I will give him a chance.

754
00:37:04.917 --> 00:37:06.833
<i>Just like giving myself a chance.</i>

755
00:37:07.875 --> 00:37:10.333
<i>We can't keep living like this anymore.</i>

756
00:37:11.750 --> 00:37:13.167
<i>He is living with his wife.</i>

757
00:37:13.250 --> 00:37:15.667
<i>someone who doesn't respect him at all.</i>

758
00:37:16.208 --> 00:37:19.167
<i>He is living in days of suffering.</i>

759
00:37:19.250 --> 00:37:22.250
<i>As for me. I told you my love story.</i>

760
00:37:22.750 --> 00:37:24.292
<i>So let me ask you this.</i>

761
00:37:24.375 --> 00:37:28.000
<i>Two miserable people who want to end their
failing relationships and come together.</i>

762
00:37:28.083 --> 00:37:29.917
<i>what's wrong with that?</i>

763
00:37:30.958 --> 00:37:32.708
<i>This issue may be controversial.</i>

764
00:37:32.792 --> 00:37:35.625
but I partly understand
why you made that decision.

765
00:37:35.708 --> 00:37:39.583
I think you met him at the intersection
of sadness and disappointment.

766
00:37:39.667 --> 00:37:42.518
And usually. that's when people feel
the deepest connection with each other.

767
00:37:42.542 --> 00:37:45.792
In the end. with eight billion people
in this world.

768
00:37:45.875 --> 00:37:48.750
no one is born with the duty
to belong to anyone forever.

769
00:37:49.333 --> 00:37:51.708
We're all independent individuals

770
00:37:51.792 --> 00:37:54.375
searching for that one fitting piece
to click with.

771
00:37:54.875 --> 00:37:57.833
<i>And I'm sorry to say this.
even husbands and wives.</i>

772
00:37:57.917 --> 00:37:59.167
<i>that marriage certificate</i>

773
00:37:59.250 --> 00:38:03.000
<i>is just a contract.
It has an expiration date.</i>

774
00:38:03.583 --> 00:38:05.208
<i>Yet so many people forget that.</i>

775
00:38:05.292 --> 00:38:07.018
<i>They think once you're married.
you're each other's forever.</i>

776
00:38:07.042 --> 00:38:08.792
<i>Girl. it doesn't work that way.</i>

777
00:38:08.875 --> 00:38:11.515
<i>If you don't hold on to what's yours.
people will come and take it.</i>

778
00:38:12.042 --> 00:38:13.542
<i>Thank you for understanding me.</i>

779
00:38:14.333 --> 00:38:18.792
And I believe if he really loves me.
he'll find a way to fix this.

780
00:38:20.167 --> 00:38:21.750
I hope so too.

781
00:38:21.833 --> 00:38:24.250
I'm actually sympathizing
with her hard right now.

782
00:38:24.333 --> 00:38:27.917
I know this is a very big decision
for you. so…

783
00:38:28.792 --> 00:38:30.083
I will not give any advice.

784
00:38:30.667 --> 00:38:32.227
<i>I just want to remind you of one thing.</i>

785
00:38:33.000 --> 00:38:35.500
<i>Every bold decision in your life</i>

786
00:38:35.583 --> 00:38:37.750
<i>will lead you to one of two outcomes.</i>

787
00:38:37.833 --> 00:38:39.125
<i>If you're right.</i>

788
00:38:39.208 --> 00:38:40.542
<i>the two of you will be happy.</i>

789
00:38:41.042 --> 00:38:44.208
However. if you're wrong.

790
00:38:44.292 --> 00:38:46.917
more than just the two of you
will end up hurting.

791
00:38:48.542 --> 00:38:52.542
I hope you'll stay clear-headed enough
to know what you need to do. and…

792
00:38:52.625 --> 00:38:54.785
I really hope everything turns out
beautifully for you.

793
00:38:54.833 --> 00:38:56.292
Good luck. sister.

794
00:38:56.792 --> 00:38:58.375
Pretty intense philosophy. huh?

795
00:38:58.458 --> 00:39:01.875
It's like she's lived ten lives
and poured them all out on this show.

796
00:39:03.500 --> 00:39:04.583
Linh…

797
00:39:08.625 --> 00:39:10.208
Do you think you are strong?

798
00:39:11.250 --> 00:39:12.583
Why do you ask me that?

799
00:39:14.583 --> 00:39:15.792
Are you happy?

800
00:39:16.542 --> 00:39:18.417
What do you mean by that?

801
00:39:19.458 --> 00:39:20.917
If you are not happy.

802
00:39:21.875 --> 00:39:23.542
would you leave your husband?

803
00:39:25.333 --> 00:39:27.208
Why is this girl so ungrateful?

804
00:39:27.292 --> 00:39:29.292
Ladies and gentlemen. I'm shocked.

805
00:39:29.375 --> 00:39:31.255
Hey. Editor. remind her.
she's talking nonsense!

806
00:39:31.292 --> 00:39:33.143
For the first time
in the history of <i>Shoulder Sister.</i>

807
00:39:33.167 --> 00:39:36.458
a guest just asked me straight to my face.

808
00:39:36.542 --> 00:39:39.625
I think I'll get a coffee
just to calm down.

809
00:39:39.708 --> 00:39:41.042
Just a moment. please.

810
00:39:42.125 --> 00:39:43.708
Now.

811
00:39:43.792 --> 00:39:45.208
Bunnie!

812
00:39:45.292 --> 00:39:47.667
Do you know why I created
the show <i>Shoulder Sister</i>?

813
00:39:48.333 --> 00:39:51.000
It's not that I'm super talented
or anything special.

814
00:39:51.083 --> 00:39:52.500
I'm just a woman.

815
00:39:52.583 --> 00:39:54.625
But I'm really lucky that I'm not weak.

816
00:39:55.208 --> 00:39:57.333
I believe I'm strong enough
and clear-headed enough

817
00:39:57.417 --> 00:40:00.375
to be a solid emotional support
for people who are struggling.

818
00:40:00.958 --> 00:40:01.958
like you right now.

819
00:40:02.667 --> 00:40:04.625
I've always chosen
to face the truth head-on.

820
00:40:05.208 --> 00:40:06.292
If…

821
00:40:06.375 --> 00:40:07.375
And I'm saying if…

822
00:40:07.917 --> 00:40:09.667
If my husband no longer loves me…

823
00:40:12.708 --> 00:40:15.542
I would never cling to someone
who doesn't love me anymore.

824
00:40:15.625 --> 00:40:17.417
I know what I'm worth.

825
00:40:17.500 --> 00:40:19.625
Yeah. are you happy with that answer?

826
00:40:19.708 --> 00:40:21.167
I'm just kidding.

827
00:40:21.250 --> 00:40:22.500
You're too funny!

828
00:40:22.583 --> 00:40:23.792
I trust you.

829
00:40:24.542 --> 00:40:25.902
You are Shoulder Sister after all.

830
00:40:27.083 --> 00:40:30.417
Okay then. anything else
you'd like to share?

831
00:40:32.292 --> 00:40:33.667
- Bunnie!
- Hey!

832
00:40:33.750 --> 00:40:35.417
Why is she taking off her mask?

833
00:40:38.667 --> 00:40:39.667
Bunnie!

834
00:40:41.333 --> 00:40:42.542
What's going on?

835
00:40:44.375 --> 00:40:45.815
Today. I will not be afraid anymore.

836
00:40:47.042 --> 00:40:49.167
I will face my decision.

837
00:40:49.250 --> 00:40:50.333
Ket!

838
00:40:50.417 --> 00:40:52.750
- Views are skyrocketing!
- Holy crap. I'm about to pass out!

839
00:40:52.833 --> 00:40:54.792
- Don't fain. Views will drop.
- Alright. I'm up.

840
00:40:54.875 --> 00:40:57.292
Do you want to know how we met?

841
00:41:11.500 --> 00:41:13.625
Oh my gosh. you just charged
at me like a bull!

842
00:41:13.708 --> 00:41:14.792
- I'm sorry.
- Le Hieu.

843
00:41:14.875 --> 00:41:16.809
why do you always bring disaster
whenever I see you?

844
00:41:16.833 --> 00:41:17.958
I'm sorry. Chairwoman.

845
00:41:18.042 --> 00:41:19.833
Ma'am. are you okay?

846
00:41:19.917 --> 00:41:21.875
- Oh. you're so cute.
- Thank you. ma'am.

847
00:41:21.958 --> 00:41:23.833
This is Nhat Ha.

848
00:41:23.917 --> 00:41:25.875
Director Phong's
new secretary. Chairwoman.

849
00:41:26.375 --> 00:41:27.708
So pretty!

850
00:41:34.750 --> 00:41:39.708
DANG THE PHONG

851
00:41:41.917 --> 00:41:42.917
TWO MONTHS AGO

852
00:41:42.958 --> 00:41:44.542
Isn't it impressive?

853
00:41:44.625 --> 00:41:46.585
We also have a lot
of interesting lights at Unios.

854
00:41:46.667 --> 00:41:49.250
Please look around.
Hieu and Giao will show the way.

855
00:41:49.333 --> 00:41:50.458
Please.

856
00:41:50.542 --> 00:41:52.208
Yes. we have hanging lights here.

857
00:41:53.208 --> 00:41:55.792
Boss. your documents are on your desk.

858
00:41:55.875 --> 00:41:58.667
Tomorrow you will fly to Japan
to attend Furniture Week.

859
00:41:58.750 --> 00:42:00.917
You'll be flying with Vietnam Airlines
at 9:30 a.m.

860
00:42:01.000 --> 00:42:03.893
When you get there. there will be a car
to take you straight to the hotel.

861
00:42:03.917 --> 00:42:05.042
So thoughtful.

862
00:42:07.667 --> 00:42:09.000
One drink!

863
00:42:09.083 --> 00:42:10.167
One for you too!

864
00:42:10.250 --> 00:42:11.625
Let me take that as well.

865
00:42:11.708 --> 00:42:14.875
Staff are supposed to take the shots
for the boss. not the other way.

866
00:42:14.958 --> 00:42:15.792
This is for you.

867
00:42:15.875 --> 00:42:17.917
- Okay. let me.
- Phong. that's nonsense.

868
00:42:18.000 --> 00:42:19.500
Can I drink with you?

869
00:42:19.583 --> 00:42:22.000
- It's okay. My employee...
- What about me?

870
00:42:22.083 --> 00:42:23.458
- Anh Duc. she's...
- I like you.

871
00:42:23.542 --> 00:42:25.268
- Phong. you can't...
- My staff doesn't know how to drink.

872
00:42:25.292 --> 00:42:26.917
If you don't drink. I'll be sad.

873
00:42:27.000 --> 00:42:28.500
We just drink together. It's nothing.

874
00:42:28.583 --> 00:42:30.125
Drink up! What's the problem?

875
00:42:37.792 --> 00:42:39.167
It's my job.

876
00:42:39.792 --> 00:42:42.083
He's the boss. he goes on business trips.

877
00:42:42.167 --> 00:42:44.417
it's normal to bring a secretary.

878
00:42:44.500 --> 00:42:47.220
Your company sure has a lot
of business trips for a lighting company.

879
00:42:47.583 --> 00:42:48.417
Don't you see that he intentionally
organized.

880
00:42:48.500 --> 00:42:49.792
- Honey.
- Business trips with you?

881
00:42:49.875 --> 00:42:51.500
Can't you see that I'm working?

882
00:42:51.583 --> 00:42:53.583
Stop picking fights.

883
00:42:53.667 --> 00:42:55.292
Go to work if you can.

884
00:42:57.083 --> 00:42:59.976
Where the hell am I supposed to find
four grand to pay them back right now?

885
00:43:00.000 --> 00:43:04.583
Everyone's gone home already.
I'm the only one left doing overtime.

886
00:43:04.667 --> 00:43:06.417
Don't you see you're cruel to me?

887
00:43:06.500 --> 00:43:07.958
Stop investing.

888
00:43:08.042 --> 00:43:10.208
You're bringing in nothing but debts.

889
00:43:10.292 --> 00:43:12.958
Stop holding me back.

890
00:43:13.042 --> 00:43:15.250
Four grand is a bit much. However…

891
00:43:15.333 --> 00:43:18.000
I can transfer you half first.
then deduct it from your salary.

892
00:43:22.708 --> 00:43:24.292
Eat something. girl!

893
00:43:24.375 --> 00:43:26.667
You go ahead. I need to finish this.

894
00:43:26.750 --> 00:43:28.000
Check it then.

895
00:43:28.083 --> 00:43:29.723
You deleted everything. What's the point?

896
00:43:29.792 --> 00:43:31.667
Your messages with him is always blank.

897
00:43:31.750 --> 00:43:34.208
If you have nothing to hide.
why would you delete it?

898
00:43:34.292 --> 00:43:36.518
I give you my phone to check.
and you say everything's wiped.

899
00:43:36.542 --> 00:43:39.333
So what exactly do I need to do
for you to trust me?

900
00:43:39.417 --> 00:43:41.625
Why do you always try
to make me the bad guy?

901
00:43:41.708 --> 00:43:44.018
Haven't we lived together long enough
to actually understand each other?

902
00:43:44.042 --> 00:43:47.083
We both have brains. Use it to think.
or are your nerves paralyzed?

903
00:43:48.250 --> 00:43:49.542
Who are you calling paralyzed?

904
00:43:52.875 --> 00:43:54.625
Who are you calling paralyzed? Huh?

905
00:43:54.708 --> 00:43:55.750
Who?

906
00:43:55.833 --> 00:43:57.667
Oh my God. oh my God. oh my God!

907
00:43:57.750 --> 00:43:58.917
You! You!

908
00:43:59.000 --> 00:44:02.333
- It's your fault you only have half a leg.
- Kim. Kim. Kim!

909
00:44:05.125 --> 00:44:06.542
Will you stop?

910
00:44:06.625 --> 00:44:08.500
I'm tired.

911
00:44:08.583 --> 00:44:12.750
I want to move out. Kim. I'm exhausted.

912
00:44:14.292 --> 00:44:15.875
Come on. everyone!

913
00:44:15.958 --> 00:44:17.798
Come and dance with me.
Why sulk in the corner?

914
00:44:18.917 --> 00:44:20.417
Come on. Mr. Khang!

915
00:44:20.500 --> 00:44:22.061
Hey. why did you push Mr. Khang. Phong?

916
00:44:22.125 --> 00:44:23.417
- Oh my gosh!
- I didn't mean to.

917
00:44:23.500 --> 00:44:24.625
So strong and fierce now?

918
00:44:24.708 --> 00:44:25.958
Let me drink it up to you!

919
00:44:26.042 --> 00:44:28.292
You're pissing on our parade. Phong.

920
00:44:28.375 --> 00:44:29.500
I fell down. Phong.

921
00:44:29.583 --> 00:44:31.333
Why are you defending her so fiercely?

922
00:44:31.417 --> 00:44:33.875
- It was an accident.
- Oh. an accident. you said?

923
00:44:33.958 --> 00:44:36.792
Then I'll just "accidentally"
won't sign this contract.

924
00:44:39.708 --> 00:44:40.792
PRESENT

925
00:44:40.875 --> 00:44:41.792
<i>Ms. Linh!</i>

926
00:44:41.875 --> 00:44:43.515
<i>- Hi there. Hieu.
- What are you doing here?</i>

927
00:44:43.583 --> 00:44:45.167
- I brought food for Phong.
- Yes.

928
00:44:45.250 --> 00:44:46.917
So romantic! Miss!

929
00:44:47.792 --> 00:44:49.542
- Have you had lunch?
- I ate already.

930
00:44:49.625 --> 00:44:50.875
Yes. thank you.

931
00:44:51.917 --> 00:44:53.875
You want a coffee?

932
00:44:53.958 --> 00:44:55.750
- Right here.
- Yes…

933
00:44:55.833 --> 00:44:57.125
- Ms. Linh...
- Honey!

934
00:45:00.125 --> 00:45:01.000
Ha.

935
00:45:01.083 --> 00:45:02.417
Meeting's over. Get back to work.

936
00:45:07.875 --> 00:45:09.667
- Hello.
- Hello.

937
00:45:09.750 --> 00:45:11.542
- Hieu!
- Yes. I'm coming.

938
00:45:17.542 --> 00:45:18.625
Sweetie!

939
00:45:20.792 --> 00:45:23.250
- Why did you suddenly come here?
- I brought you food.

940
00:45:24.542 --> 00:45:26.708
Did I hear that right?

941
00:45:26.792 --> 00:45:28.667
This is normally my job.

942
00:45:28.750 --> 00:45:29.917
Surprised?

943
00:45:30.000 --> 00:45:31.042
Obviously!

944
00:45:31.125 --> 00:45:32.917
MC Hai Linh brought me food!

945
00:45:33.750 --> 00:45:34.750
Who was that?

946
00:45:34.833 --> 00:45:35.833
My staff.

947
00:45:36.375 --> 00:45:37.500
Why is she crying?

948
00:45:38.958 --> 00:45:40.393
Her work hasn't been up to par recently.

949
00:45:40.417 --> 00:45:42.250
Family pressure or something.

950
00:45:42.333 --> 00:45:44.000
Can't even handle a bit of scolding.

951
00:45:44.083 --> 00:45:47.292
Why do you talk with her
behind closed doors?

952
00:45:47.375 --> 00:45:48.958
Normally. you hate being cramped.

953
00:45:49.042 --> 00:45:50.750
It was too sunny. so I closed the blinds.

954
00:45:53.917 --> 00:45:54.958
Staff?

955
00:45:56.042 --> 00:45:58.167
- Secretary.
- Ah. secretary.

956
00:45:58.250 --> 00:45:59.625
I've never heard of her.

957
00:45:59.708 --> 00:46:01.750
Just an ordinary secretary.

958
00:46:01.833 --> 00:46:03.708
nothing special. Why would I tell you?

959
00:46:04.750 --> 00:46:05.958
Is her name Bunnie?

960
00:46:07.583 --> 00:46:08.875
I don't know.

961
00:46:08.958 --> 00:46:10.333
Her name is Nhat Ha.

962
00:46:11.417 --> 00:46:12.958
- Do you know her?
- Yeah.

963
00:46:13.042 --> 00:46:14.458
She was a guest on my show.

964
00:46:18.208 --> 00:46:19.667
So surprising.

965
00:46:20.333 --> 00:46:22.208
Why did my staff come on your show?

966
00:46:22.292 --> 00:46:23.667
To tell her story. of course.

967
00:46:27.250 --> 00:46:29.208
So? Is there anything you want to tell me?

968
00:46:30.375 --> 00:46:31.708
Any story for me?

969
00:46:33.375 --> 00:46:34.708
Why do you suddenly ask?

970
00:46:37.583 --> 00:46:39.333
Okay. let me tell you.

971
00:46:40.208 --> 00:46:42.042
She said she just broke up with her ex.

972
00:46:42.583 --> 00:46:44.000
Dating someone new now.

973
00:46:44.583 --> 00:46:45.875
Very happy.

974
00:46:45.958 --> 00:46:47.319
What does that have to do with me?

975
00:46:51.625 --> 00:46:53.458
She said she's dating her boss.

976
00:46:54.542 --> 00:46:57.083
Why would my staff go on your show
and say such a bizarre thing?

977
00:46:58.250 --> 00:47:01.042
I've asked you so many questions.
so you can tell me the truth.

978
00:47:01.125 --> 00:47:02.625
You had your chance.

979
00:47:03.250 --> 00:47:05.042
I'm your wife. Phong.

980
00:47:05.125 --> 00:47:06.625
I'm not a kid.

981
00:47:08.542 --> 00:47:09.833
I'm so disappointed in you.

982
00:47:12.875 --> 00:47:14.333
I want a divorce.

983
00:47:15.292 --> 00:47:16.542
Linh! Linh! Listen to me!

984
00:47:18.333 --> 00:47:19.417
Linh!

985
00:47:19.500 --> 00:47:20.500
Linh!

986
00:47:21.958 --> 00:47:23.875
Can we sit down and talk for a bit?

987
00:47:23.958 --> 00:47:25.208
Sir. ma'am.

988
00:47:27.500 --> 00:47:28.750
What's going on?

989
00:47:33.583 --> 00:47:34.976
What do you want to do with the new house?

990
00:47:35.000 --> 00:47:36.417
You want it. or should I take it

991
00:47:36.500 --> 00:47:37.542
and transfer you the cash?

992
00:47:37.625 --> 00:47:39.917
No. Linh. I want to talk
to resolve this together.

993
00:47:40.000 --> 00:47:41.583
Not this kind of resolution.

994
00:47:41.667 --> 00:47:43.792
- Are you really gonna divorce me?
- Correct.

995
00:47:43.875 --> 00:47:45.333
- Adultery means divorce.
- Oh my God!

996
00:47:45.417 --> 00:47:46.750
Then why did we get married?

997
00:47:46.833 --> 00:47:50.417
If we should just date. argue. then split.
what's the point of getting married then?

998
00:47:50.500 --> 00:47:52.976
How can the word "divorce"
just roll off your tongue so easily?

999
00:47:53.000 --> 00:47:55.958
Even if I had an affair. would you
at least bother to ask why I did it?

1000
00:47:56.042 --> 00:47:58.184
Adultery is adultery.
What's the point of knowing more?

1001
00:47:58.208 --> 00:48:00.500
- Is Phong having an affair?
- I'm not.

1002
00:48:00.583 --> 00:48:02.864
I was explaining to my wife.
but she doesn't listen to me.

1003
00:48:03.042 --> 00:48:04.042
Well. let him talk.

1004
00:48:09.042 --> 00:48:09.958
You have five minutes.

1005
00:48:10.042 --> 00:48:11.667
I'm not a guest on your show.

1006
00:48:12.292 --> 00:48:13.583
I am your husband.

1007
00:48:14.167 --> 00:48:15.726
- How can I talk like that...
- Thirty seconds gone.

1008
00:48:15.750 --> 00:48:17.750
Hey! You're being unreasonable!

1009
00:48:17.833 --> 00:48:20.208
You can't time a couple's conversation.

1010
00:48:20.292 --> 00:48:21.542
How can he say anything?

1011
00:48:21.625 --> 00:48:22.768
Is this a debate competition?

1012
00:48:22.792 --> 00:48:24.500
Go ahead. Say what you need to say.

1013
00:48:24.583 --> 00:48:26.667
Ian. this is our problem.

1014
00:48:27.208 --> 00:48:29.000
Can you let us deal with it privately...

1015
00:48:29.083 --> 00:48:30.917
No way! I'll resolve it for you guys.

1016
00:48:31.000 --> 00:48:33.458
I'm super fair.
I'd never take her side blindly.

1017
00:48:33.542 --> 00:48:35.250
Tell me. who is she jealous of?

1018
00:48:36.125 --> 00:48:38.875
Nhat Ha. my secretary.

1019
00:48:38.958 --> 00:48:42.125
Oh my gosh. that girl
is so decent. I've met her.

1020
00:48:42.208 --> 00:48:43.833
She's not as pretty as you.

1021
00:48:43.917 --> 00:48:45.667
Have you watched the Bunnie episode?

1022
00:48:45.750 --> 00:48:47.726
She came back for a second show.
Have you watched that?

1023
00:48:47.750 --> 00:48:50.708
My husband just left me.
I'm not in the mood to watch anything.

1024
00:48:50.792 --> 00:48:52.917
She came on.
said she dumped her boyfriend.

1025
00:48:53.000 --> 00:48:54.042
Now she's dating her boss.

1026
00:48:54.125 --> 00:48:55.542
Whoops. that's you!

1027
00:48:55.625 --> 00:48:57.125
Ian! It's not true!

1028
00:48:57.208 --> 00:48:58.417
What the heck!

1029
00:48:59.542 --> 00:49:01.833
It might sound a bit funny
when I say this.

1030
00:49:01.917 --> 00:49:03.208
You must believe me.

1031
00:49:03.875 --> 00:49:05.083
Linh!

1032
00:49:07.833 --> 00:49:09.208
She's harassing me.

1033
00:49:12.458 --> 00:49:13.958
Hieu. Giao. show them around.

1034
00:49:17.083 --> 00:49:18.250
Boss.

1035
00:49:19.417 --> 00:49:20.958
Have you had dinner yet?

1036
00:49:21.042 --> 00:49:22.083
Not yet.

1037
00:49:22.167 --> 00:49:25.125
I know this nice steak restaurant.
Can we go eat?

1038
00:49:25.208 --> 00:49:27.125
You go ahead. I'm having dinner
with my wife.

1039
00:49:27.708 --> 00:49:28.708
Enjoy!

1040
00:49:29.750 --> 00:49:31.042
You're still here?

1041
00:49:32.042 --> 00:49:32.958
Why are you crying?

1042
00:49:33.042 --> 00:49:35.000
My boyfriend just told me he's 4k in debt.

1043
00:49:35.667 --> 00:49:37.167
Can you give me an advanced salary?

1044
00:49:37.250 --> 00:49:39.125
If not. the gang will kill him.

1045
00:49:40.917 --> 00:49:43.167
Four grand is a bit much. but…

1046
00:49:43.250 --> 00:49:44.625
I can give you half in advance.

1047
00:49:45.667 --> 00:49:46.667
Thank you. boss.

1048
00:49:48.792 --> 00:49:50.000
What are you doing. Ha?

1049
00:49:50.083 --> 00:49:51.792
I know you like me too.

1050
00:49:52.500 --> 00:49:54.042
I've seen you checking me out...

1051
00:49:54.125 --> 00:49:56.250
Do you know what you're talking about?

1052
00:49:56.333 --> 00:49:57.750
You're losing control.

1053
00:49:57.833 --> 00:49:59.083
- Boss!
- Don't do that again.

1054
00:49:59.167 --> 00:50:00.208
Boss!

1055
00:50:00.292 --> 00:50:01.292
Boss!

1056
00:50:04.333 --> 00:50:05.333
Where have you been?

1057
00:50:05.417 --> 00:50:09.042
You didn't reply to my texts.
didn't answer my calls.

1058
00:50:09.125 --> 00:50:10.285
You didn't go to work either.

1059
00:50:10.333 --> 00:50:12.458
I didn't know where to find you.

1060
00:50:12.542 --> 00:50:14.875
I'm your secretary. I know your schedule.

1061
00:50:14.958 --> 00:50:16.875
You weren't busy with anything else.

1062
00:50:17.458 --> 00:50:19.167
She is unstable.

1063
00:50:19.250 --> 00:50:20.730
I saved all the evidence. Look at it.

1064
00:50:21.083 --> 00:50:21.917
See?

1065
00:50:22.000 --> 00:50:23.250
Is this girl mental?

1066
00:50:23.333 --> 00:50:25.000
Messaging and ringing you non-stop?

1067
00:50:25.083 --> 00:50:26.542
Well. you must have done something.

1068
00:50:26.625 --> 00:50:28.417
I didn't do anything to her.

1069
00:50:28.500 --> 00:50:30.208
To me. Ha is a decent employee.

1070
00:50:30.292 --> 00:50:31.125
She is good at her job.

1071
00:50:31.208 --> 00:50:32.750
Lately. her performance went down.

1072
00:50:32.833 --> 00:50:36.042
Turns out it's family and love issues.

1073
00:50:36.625 --> 00:50:37.976
I only gave her some advice. that's all.

1074
00:50:38.000 --> 00:50:40.542
How was I supposed to know
that she likes me?

1075
00:50:40.625 --> 00:50:42.750
The moment I found out.
I straight-up rejected her.

1076
00:50:42.833 --> 00:50:44.333
I didn't even reply to her messages.

1077
00:50:44.417 --> 00:50:45.833
You have to fire her.

1078
00:50:45.917 --> 00:50:47.167
I did this morning.

1079
00:50:47.250 --> 00:50:48.333
He fired her.

1080
00:50:48.958 --> 00:50:50.018
Do you want me to call her now?

1081
00:50:50.042 --> 00:50:52.625
Don't do that. I have no reason
to talk to her.

1082
00:50:52.708 --> 00:50:54.628
- I'll call her then.
- Stop that. I don't like it.

1083
00:50:55.167 --> 00:50:57.367
Why are you so aggressive?
Who are you even acting like?

1084
00:50:57.542 --> 00:50:58.625
I haven't done anything!

1085
00:50:58.708 --> 00:51:00.042
You refuse to call her.

1086
00:51:00.125 --> 00:51:02.458
You don't trust my explanation.
What do you want me to do?

1087
00:51:02.542 --> 00:51:03.893
What. you just eat up whatever she said?

1088
00:51:03.917 --> 00:51:05.667
I just believe what I see.

1089
00:51:05.750 --> 00:51:07.292
What did you see?

1090
00:51:07.375 --> 00:51:10.083
How much truth
do you really think you caught?

1091
00:51:10.750 --> 00:51:13.375
I don't know what bullshit
she spun on the show.

1092
00:51:13.458 --> 00:51:15.139
All I'm doing is trying to explain to you.

1093
00:51:15.208 --> 00:51:17.583
but you won't listen to me.
You'd rather believe a stranger.

1094
00:51:22.625 --> 00:51:23.625
Linh!

1095
00:51:25.792 --> 00:51:27.500
How have I been to you all these years?

1096
00:51:28.167 --> 00:51:31.417
Did I treat you so badly?
How come you have no faith in me?

1097
00:51:33.375 --> 00:51:34.976
In your eyes. what kind of husband am I?

1098
00:51:35.292 --> 00:51:36.292
Tell me.

1099
00:51:36.917 --> 00:51:38.458
How have I been as your husband?

1100
00:51:41.500 --> 00:51:42.750
You are a good husband.

1101
00:51:43.375 --> 00:51:45.083
Even a perfect one.

1102
00:51:45.667 --> 00:51:47.875
But my rule is simple.
Once there's cheating. it's over.

1103
00:51:47.958 --> 00:51:49.292
To hell with your rule.

1104
00:51:49.875 --> 00:51:53.042
All our conversations
are just "principles" and "rules".

1105
00:51:53.125 --> 00:51:55.086
Don't you realize our relationship
is in distress?

1106
00:51:55.125 --> 00:51:55.958
What distress?

1107
00:51:56.042 --> 00:51:59.208
We're still happy. no fight or anything.
We just came back from vacation.

1108
00:51:59.292 --> 00:52:01.917
The problem is. you don't even see
that we're having issues.

1109
00:52:06.917 --> 00:52:09.583
Ever since we got married.
every time we fight.

1110
00:52:09.667 --> 00:52:11.958
have we ever talked
for more than five minutes?

1111
00:52:12.708 --> 00:52:14.542
Or is it always you talking
and me listening.

1112
00:52:14.625 --> 00:52:16.601
and the second I try to speak.
you either don't listen

1113
00:52:16.625 --> 00:52:17.792
or cut me off?

1114
00:52:19.083 --> 00:52:21.667
Did you call me a perfect husband?

1115
00:52:21.750 --> 00:52:22.583
Thank you.

1116
00:52:22.667 --> 00:52:25.208
But I wasn't born perfect.

1117
00:52:25.292 --> 00:52:26.917
I have to work for it.

1118
00:52:27.000 --> 00:52:28.667
I have to love you. love this family.

1119
00:52:28.750 --> 00:52:32.375
I work every single day to earn
the "perfect" that you want.

1120
00:52:33.208 --> 00:52:34.292
What about you?

1121
00:52:34.375 --> 00:52:36.292
Have you ever asked yourself
the same question?

1122
00:52:38.250 --> 00:52:40.458
Have you given me the wife I wanted?

1123
00:52:42.542 --> 00:52:43.875
Now I want to know.

1124
00:52:44.708 --> 00:52:46.083
How have I been as your wife?

1125
00:52:46.792 --> 00:52:48.458
Did I do something wrong?

1126
00:52:48.542 --> 00:52:50.125
What did I do wrong?

1127
00:52:51.042 --> 00:52:53.458
No. You're not wrong.

1128
00:52:55.750 --> 00:52:57.375
You can never see that you're wrong.

1129
00:52:59.500 --> 00:53:01.875
You created a show to listen
to everyone in the world.

1130
00:53:02.833 --> 00:53:05.125
but there's one person you refuse to hear.

1131
00:53:06.417 --> 00:53:07.708
Your husband.

1132
00:53:08.333 --> 00:53:10.167
I never wanted a super-talented wife

1133
00:53:10.250 --> 00:53:12.250
or one who's always busy working.

1134
00:53:12.333 --> 00:53:14.625
I just want you to love me a bit.

1135
00:53:14.708 --> 00:53:16.042
listen to me a bit.

1136
00:53:17.583 --> 00:53:19.458
pay attention to my feelings a bit.

1137
00:53:22.167 --> 00:53:24.292
We can't even talk to each other.

1138
00:53:26.958 --> 00:53:29.833
I feel so lonely in our relationship.

1139
00:53:32.958 --> 00:53:34.667
If all you want right now is a divorce.

1140
00:53:34.750 --> 00:53:36.551
and you're not willing
to figure anything out…

1141
00:53:39.250 --> 00:53:40.450
Go ahead and do what you want.

1142
00:53:43.542 --> 00:53:45.833
Phong's actually right about this one.

1143
00:53:46.458 --> 00:53:48.083
You're savage as hell too.

1144
00:53:48.167 --> 00:53:51.125
Does anyone ever really see
their own faults in a relationship?

1145
00:53:51.625 --> 00:53:52.958
Linh!

1146
00:53:53.542 --> 00:53:55.125
Phong. something's wrong with her!

1147
00:53:55.208 --> 00:53:56.333
Linh!

1148
00:53:56.417 --> 00:53:58.208
Linh! Linh! Linh!

1149
00:54:01.583 --> 00:54:02.833
Take the pills.

1150
00:54:02.917 --> 00:54:04.250
Give it to me.

1151
00:54:05.083 --> 00:54:07.708
Open your mouth.
Take the medicine and go to sleep.

1152
00:54:07.792 --> 00:54:09.417
Oh my gosh. you're so aggressive.

1153
00:54:09.500 --> 00:54:13.208
One bit of stress and your whole body
seizes up. So why are you still so angry?

1154
00:54:13.292 --> 00:54:14.542
Okay. let her get some sleep...

1155
00:54:14.625 --> 00:54:17.500
No. I have to say it. It's hard on her.
What if it happens again?

1156
00:54:17.583 --> 00:54:20.708
I got it. You go back to sleep.
I'll be here. okay?

1157
00:54:20.792 --> 00:54:21.792
Fine. I got it.

1158
00:54:21.875 --> 00:54:23.792
It's my house.
You don't have to kick me out.

1159
00:54:23.875 --> 00:54:25.917
You focus on taking care of your wife.

1160
00:54:26.000 --> 00:54:27.583
Always sister this. sister that.

1161
00:54:27.667 --> 00:54:30.042
but wouldn't hesitate to kick me out
for alone time.

1162
00:54:31.250 --> 00:54:32.458
Linh…

1163
00:54:36.458 --> 00:54:37.542
Trust me.

1164
00:54:39.667 --> 00:54:41.708
I never did anything wrong to you.

1165
00:54:44.167 --> 00:54:46.583
That girl. Ha. I think
she has mental problems.

1166
00:54:47.375 --> 00:54:48.625
But I fired her.

1167
00:54:49.542 --> 00:54:51.792
From now on. you don't
have to worry about her anymore.

1168
00:54:55.875 --> 00:54:58.167
Relax. Don't think about it.

1169
00:54:58.250 --> 00:54:59.417
Get some sleep.

1170
00:54:59.500 --> 00:55:01.226
I'll take a shower.
then come sleep with you.

1171
00:55:01.250 --> 00:55:02.458
You sleep downstairs.

1172
00:55:03.208 --> 00:55:04.042
Huh?

1173
00:55:04.125 --> 00:55:06.000
I'll sleep alone.
You go and sleep downstairs.

1174
00:55:14.500 --> 00:55:15.667
Oh. here's your ring.

1175
00:55:16.708 --> 00:55:17.792
I'll leave it here.

1176
00:55:18.750 --> 00:55:20.083
Put it away. Don't lose it.

1177
00:55:21.375 --> 00:55:23.000
Don't think about it anymore.

1178
00:55:23.083 --> 00:55:24.333
Goodnight. my dear.

1179
00:55:43.708 --> 00:55:45.309
So much for not going through his phone.

1180
00:55:45.833 --> 00:55:47.250
You go straight for the laptop.

1181
00:55:47.958 --> 00:55:49.708
See if he has any hidden folders.

1182
00:55:56.667 --> 00:55:57.667
Nothing?

1183
00:55:57.708 --> 00:56:01.125
Any private group chat on Viber or Zalo?

1184
00:56:02.833 --> 00:56:04.583
Still nothing?

1185
00:56:04.667 --> 00:56:08.583
Just go check the search history.
We'll know from the recent searches.

1186
00:56:12.792 --> 00:56:14.625
HOW TO GET RID OF A STALKER

1187
00:56:14.708 --> 00:56:17.000
DEPENDENT PERSONALITY DISORDER DPD

1188
00:56:18.417 --> 00:56:21.042
Linh. I have goosebumps.

1189
00:56:21.125 --> 00:56:23.750
I didn't expect her to be a sicko
with that pretty face.

1190
00:56:24.417 --> 00:56:25.708
I mean. it's understandable.

1191
00:56:25.792 --> 00:56:27.458
Phong is handsome. wealthy.

1192
00:56:28.042 --> 00:56:30.125
plus he's her boss. How could she resist?

1193
00:57:16.292 --> 00:57:18.000
CALLING BOSS

1194
00:57:25.625 --> 00:57:28.625
MOBILE
NHAT HA (SECRETARY)

1195
00:57:29.375 --> 00:57:30.583
RECENT
BOSS (52)

1196
00:57:45.542 --> 00:57:47.309
Thank you for your dedication
and contributions

1197
00:57:47.333 --> 00:57:49.750
to the company during your time with us.

1198
00:58:17.917 --> 00:58:19.083
Bunnie.

1199
00:58:20.208 --> 00:58:21.583
Bunnie. open the door.

1200
00:58:23.167 --> 00:58:25.708
I kept my promise.
I haven't bothered you at all for a month.

1201
00:58:25.792 --> 00:58:27.375
Can we talk?

1202
00:58:28.458 --> 00:58:30.143
I've thought it through.
I can't live without you.

1203
00:58:30.167 --> 00:58:32.125
Can we talk a little bit now. Bunnie?

1204
00:58:32.792 --> 00:58:34.042
Please stop hiding from me.

1205
00:58:38.958 --> 00:58:40.792
Bunnie. don't make me pry
the door open again.

1206
00:58:44.042 --> 00:58:45.667
Bunnie!

1207
00:58:46.375 --> 00:58:48.750
Why would you order.
then not pick up your phone?

1208
00:58:48.833 --> 00:58:50.059
I've been ringing the doorbell too.

1209
00:58:50.083 --> 00:58:52.083
I have other orders to deliver.

1210
00:58:52.167 --> 00:58:53.375
Sorry.

1211
00:58:53.458 --> 00:58:54.542
Are you alright?

1212
00:58:55.458 --> 00:58:56.792
What the heck?

1213
00:58:57.375 --> 00:58:58.458
Are you insane?

1214
00:58:58.542 --> 00:59:00.000
Do you know what time it is?

1215
00:59:00.083 --> 00:59:01.417
Why won't you let me sleep?

1216
00:59:01.500 --> 00:59:03.833
She moved out a month ago.

1217
00:59:03.917 --> 00:59:05.042
Are you looking for a ghost?

1218
00:59:05.125 --> 00:59:08.083
- She moved out a month ago?
- Yep. all moved.

1219
00:59:08.167 --> 00:59:09.292
Why are you so stubborn?

1220
00:59:10.042 --> 00:59:12.292
I can't sleep… I have constant headaches.

1221
00:59:12.375 --> 00:59:13.792
Look at me now.

1222
00:59:13.875 --> 00:59:15.958
I'm pretty. but I'm lifeless.

1223
00:59:16.042 --> 00:59:17.417
- Now...
- Sorry.

1224
00:59:17.500 --> 00:59:18.917
What do you mean sorry?

1225
00:59:19.667 --> 00:59:21.875
She's so pretty and full of life.

1226
00:59:21.958 --> 00:59:23.125
Look at you!

1227
00:59:23.208 --> 00:59:24.583
Only a leg and a half.

1228
00:59:35.292 --> 00:59:36.833
What did you just say?

1229
00:59:39.417 --> 00:59:42.458
It's just a misunderstanding.
Just checking in. that's all.

1230
00:59:42.542 --> 00:59:44.000
That gift box is so beautiful.

1231
00:59:44.083 --> 00:59:47.583
Go to sleep. Maybe your leg
will grow back in the morning.

1232
00:59:47.667 --> 00:59:49.625
It's late. I'm off to bed.

1233
00:59:49.708 --> 00:59:50.917
Bye.

1234
01:00:13.917 --> 01:00:15.792
<i>Have you ever asked yourself
the same question?</i>

1235
01:00:15.875 --> 01:00:18.042
Have you given me the wife I wanted?

1236
01:00:18.125 --> 01:00:21.000
<i>Don't you realize our relationship
is struggling?</i>

1237
01:00:21.083 --> 01:00:22.458
What are you even filming?

1238
01:00:22.542 --> 01:00:24.625
I specifically told you
to wait for good lighting!

1239
01:00:24.708 --> 01:00:25.851
Do you need to get this worked up?

1240
01:00:25.875 --> 01:00:27.958
How can I not get upset
when it looks this bad?

1241
01:00:29.250 --> 01:00:31.684
- What if there's someone here?
- No one's here. plus we haven't done it...

1242
01:00:31.708 --> 01:00:33.917
I said stop!

1243
01:00:34.000 --> 01:00:35.792
- Baby!
- What a pervert!

1244
01:00:36.333 --> 01:00:37.833
Let's head back! Pull up your pants.

1245
01:00:37.917 --> 01:00:38.917
Linh!

1246
01:00:39.000 --> 01:00:40.792
- Welcome back.
- Hello!

1247
01:00:40.875 --> 01:00:42.083
Get ready for dinner.

1248
01:00:42.167 --> 01:00:43.708
It's gonna be so good. Come in.

1249
01:00:44.917 --> 01:00:46.625
<i>There is no one
as perfect as your husband.</i>

1250
01:00:47.917 --> 01:00:49.226
- Stop. Ian is calling us.
- Let her be.

1251
01:00:49.250 --> 01:00:50.750
They need us downstairs.

1252
01:00:50.833 --> 01:00:51.833
Stop!

1253
01:00:51.917 --> 01:00:53.000
Can't you hear me?

1254
01:00:53.083 --> 01:00:54.625
When I say let go. let go.

1255
01:00:54.708 --> 01:00:57.417
I really hate when someone restrains
my arms and legs.

1256
01:00:58.083 --> 01:01:00.458
<i>But my rule is simple.
Once there's cheating. it's over.</i>

1257
01:01:00.542 --> 01:01:01.375
<i>To hell with your rules.</i>

1258
01:01:01.458 --> 01:01:03.018
<i>All our conversations
are just "principles" and "rules".</i>

1259
01:01:03.042 --> 01:01:04.476
<i>How much truth
do you really think you caught?</i>

1260
01:01:04.500 --> 01:01:06.601
- What did I do wrong?
- You can never see that you're wrong.

1261
01:01:06.625 --> 01:01:08.458
<i>I feel so lonely in our relationship.</i>

1262
01:01:29.208 --> 01:01:31.083
Hey. kiddo!

1263
01:01:31.167 --> 01:01:33.500
Daddy. where are you?

1264
01:01:33.583 --> 01:01:35.500
<i>Ah! I'm at your grandma's house.</i>

1265
01:01:35.583 --> 01:01:36.750
Do you miss me?

1266
01:01:36.833 --> 01:01:38.500
I miss you so much.

1267
01:01:38.583 --> 01:01:40.917
Do you miss me and mom?

1268
01:01:41.000 --> 01:01:42.458
Of course.

1269
01:01:42.542 --> 01:01:44.417
When are you coming home?

1270
01:01:44.500 --> 01:01:46.708
<i>I'm working so far away.
I can't come home yet.</i>

1271
01:01:48.000 --> 01:01:49.917
But how did you know how to call me?

1272
01:01:50.000 --> 01:01:51.042
<i>Um…</i>

1273
01:01:51.625 --> 01:01:53.458
<i>Mom told me to call.</i>

1274
01:01:54.375 --> 01:01:56.875
- Don't say that.
- I'm not allowed to say that.

1275
01:01:56.958 --> 01:01:58.292
Hey!

1276
01:01:59.292 --> 01:02:00.458
Is Mom sitting next to you?

1277
01:02:02.167 --> 01:02:03.250
<i>Ask Mom if she's okay.</i>

1278
01:02:03.333 --> 01:02:05.708
I'm dead. Don't pretend
like you love me so much.

1279
01:02:05.792 --> 01:02:07.458
Mom said she was dead.

1280
01:02:09.083 --> 01:02:11.375
Damn. that was so embarrassing.

1281
01:02:11.458 --> 01:02:13.226
I told you to practice first.
but you didn't listen.

1282
01:02:13.250 --> 01:02:15.542
I've practiced many times.
but she keeps adding words.

1283
01:02:15.625 --> 01:02:17.333
Such a cute little screenwriter.

1284
01:02:17.417 --> 01:02:18.792
You get all the things you want.

1285
01:02:18.875 --> 01:02:20.542
yet you can't help your mother at all.

1286
01:02:31.958 --> 01:02:33.000
Oh. my goodness! Son!

1287
01:02:33.083 --> 01:02:34.643
Are you pooping with the door unlocked?

1288
01:02:34.667 --> 01:02:35.833
I forgot. Close it. Dad.

1289
01:02:35.917 --> 01:02:37.208
Disgusting.

1290
01:02:43.542 --> 01:02:44.583
Hey!

1291
01:02:44.667 --> 01:02:46.542
- Ian called. didn't she?
- Dad…

1292
01:02:47.042 --> 01:02:48.792
I know. I know.

1293
01:02:48.875 --> 01:02:50.500
It's good that she called.

1294
01:02:51.958 --> 01:02:53.167
Keep pooping.

1295
01:03:14.417 --> 01:03:16.750
Uncle Thang. Auntie Lam.

1296
01:03:16.833 --> 01:03:19.375
- Come in.
- Is that Thu? Come on in.

1297
01:03:19.458 --> 01:03:20.978
I brought some gifts from my hometown.

1298
01:03:21.042 --> 01:03:22.375
Wow. so cool!

1299
01:03:23.125 --> 01:03:24.250
- Thank you.
- No worries.

1300
01:03:24.333 --> 01:03:26.375
Oh. and by the way. thank you again.

1301
01:03:26.458 --> 01:03:28.625
Because you keep confiding in Son.

1302
01:03:28.708 --> 01:03:32.292
he has moved back home with us
for more than a month already.

1303
01:03:32.375 --> 01:03:33.417
- Dad!
- Oh!

1304
01:03:33.500 --> 01:03:35.000
Was she really mad at me?

1305
01:03:35.083 --> 01:03:36.167
Why is she mad at me?

1306
01:03:36.250 --> 01:03:37.750
She has issues.

1307
01:03:37.833 --> 01:03:39.667
You know that she's the jealous type.

1308
01:03:39.750 --> 01:03:41.542
Last time she called. you didn't pick up.

1309
01:03:41.625 --> 01:03:43.208
I was in the bathroom.

1310
01:03:43.292 --> 01:03:44.500
Is that not allowed?

1311
01:03:44.583 --> 01:03:46.000
It's a basic human need.

1312
01:03:46.083 --> 01:03:48.000
She also didn't say anything
when I picked up.

1313
01:03:48.083 --> 01:03:49.792
She was mental at that point.

1314
01:03:49.875 --> 01:03:52.309
Don't worry about it. It's a good thing
she didn't say anything.

1315
01:03:52.333 --> 01:03:53.518
She would've cursed you in the face.

1316
01:03:53.542 --> 01:03:55.268
Well. it's a good thing
she didn't curse at me.

1317
01:03:55.292 --> 01:03:56.625
I would've returned the favor.

1318
01:03:56.708 --> 01:03:58.208
- Oh come on!
- Thu. I'm begging you.

1319
01:03:58.792 --> 01:03:59.917
You weren't in the right.

1320
01:04:00.500 --> 01:04:03.625
You could've talked to anyone.
yet you chose my son so late at night.

1321
01:04:03.708 --> 01:04:04.875
driving his wife crazy.

1322
01:04:04.958 --> 01:04:07.167
- Well. I was sad.
- Still not an excuse.

1323
01:04:07.250 --> 01:04:08.625
And you. Son.

1324
01:04:08.708 --> 01:04:09.833
Just save her name as it is.

1325
01:04:09.917 --> 01:04:12.583
Why the +Th? Of course. your wife
is gonna be jealous.

1326
01:04:15.458 --> 01:04:17.000
Listen to me.

1327
01:04:17.083 --> 01:04:18.750
You go back to Ian.

1328
01:04:18.833 --> 01:04:21.625
No one can stand
your crazy personality except her.

1329
01:04:22.208 --> 01:04:23.667
I noticed something.

1330
01:04:23.750 --> 01:04:26.708
Anyone named Ian and Lam are good people.

1331
01:04:26.792 --> 01:04:28.542
Listen to your mother. Son.

1332
01:04:28.625 --> 01:04:30.333
Look at me and learn.

1333
01:04:30.417 --> 01:04:31.833
- Learn what?
- Oh. nothing.

1334
01:04:31.917 --> 01:04:32.917
It's nothing.

1335
01:04:32.958 --> 01:04:34.792
You guys are fighting. My cue to leave.

1336
01:04:34.875 --> 01:04:36.875
As for you. go back to your wife.

1337
01:04:36.958 --> 01:04:39.167
Don't blame me if you get a divorce.

1338
01:04:39.250 --> 01:04:41.458
I'm begging you. crazy kid.

1339
01:04:42.042 --> 01:04:44.667
- Don't visit too much. alright?
- She arrived like a gust.

1340
01:04:44.750 --> 01:04:47.333
then vanished like a raging storm.

1341
01:04:47.417 --> 01:04:48.750
Insane!

1342
01:04:56.417 --> 01:04:57.792
Linh?

1343
01:04:57.875 --> 01:05:00.417
Why are you out here?
Everything is ready for you.

1344
01:05:01.333 --> 01:05:03.208
- Ket!
- Yes?

1345
01:05:03.792 --> 01:05:05.125
What if I…

1346
01:05:06.208 --> 01:05:07.833
What if I say I want a divorce?

1347
01:05:09.250 --> 01:05:11.167
I almost swallowed my candy.

1348
01:05:11.750 --> 01:05:13.292
I'm just asking. Just… what if.

1349
01:05:13.375 --> 01:05:14.542
What if. right?

1350
01:05:14.625 --> 01:05:16.458
If one day you want a divorce.

1351
01:05:16.542 --> 01:05:19.559
you first push me down these stairs.
wait till I'm dead. then do what you want.

1352
01:05:19.583 --> 01:05:21.375
Oh my God. there are a bunch of ads.

1353
01:05:21.458 --> 01:05:23.625
a bunch of contracts we're gonna sign.

1354
01:05:23.708 --> 01:05:26.625
You two look so perfect
and happy in public.

1355
01:05:26.708 --> 01:05:29.059
everyone's admiring you like crazy.
and now you want a divorce?

1356
01:05:29.083 --> 01:05:32.042
So this old chick gets stuck
carrying everything. drowning in debt?

1357
01:05:32.125 --> 01:05:33.833
Crazy question!

1358
01:05:33.917 --> 01:05:34.750
But what's wrong?

1359
01:05:34.833 --> 01:05:39.042
It's just a little bickering here
and there. Why jump straight to divorce?

1360
01:05:39.542 --> 01:05:41.792
Did something happen? Tell me.

1361
01:05:43.375 --> 01:05:44.917
Ket. it's time.

1362
01:05:45.000 --> 01:05:47.208
- For what?
- For the next episode.

1363
01:05:47.292 --> 01:05:50.000
Say a full sentence next time.

1364
01:05:50.083 --> 01:05:52.542
What the heck? It's the Owl's episode.

1365
01:05:52.625 --> 01:05:55.417
- Who?
- The Owl! The Owl!

1366
01:05:55.500 --> 01:05:57.375
Ah. my gosh. the owl.

1367
01:05:57.458 --> 01:05:59.750
That's right. The Owl has a great story!

1368
01:05:59.833 --> 01:06:01.542
Listen to me. Let's go shoot it.

1369
01:06:01.625 --> 01:06:02.792
We'll talk later.

1370
01:06:02.875 --> 01:06:03.708
Let's get ready.

1371
01:06:03.792 --> 01:06:05.309
Damn sis. you forgot everything
I said. Zero cooperation.

1372
01:06:05.333 --> 01:06:07.833
Sorry. sorry. should I kneel down as well?

1373
01:06:09.625 --> 01:06:12.292
<i>Ladies and gentelmen.</i>
<i>welcome back to</i> Shoulder Sister.

1374
01:06:13.000 --> 01:06:14.667
<i>Okay. let's continue with our Owl.</i>

1375
01:06:14.750 --> 01:06:17.101
<i>Let's circle back to your wife
being quite an extreme person.</i>

1376
01:06:17.125 --> 01:06:21.125
<i>She loves you. but her love makes her
an extremely jealous person.</i>

1377
01:06:21.208 --> 01:06:23.542
She does all sorts of crazy things.
stressing you out.

1378
01:06:23.625 --> 01:06:27.708
So why do you still choose
to be with someone like that. Mr. Owl?

1379
01:06:27.792 --> 01:06:29.833
Well… It's because…

1380
01:06:30.833 --> 01:06:31.750
<i>I love her.</i>

1381
01:06:31.833 --> 01:06:34.292
Oh my gosh. it's so cheesy.
like a K-drama.

1382
01:06:34.375 --> 01:06:35.500
He seems sincere.

1383
01:06:35.583 --> 01:06:38.500
I believe him. I always
believe handsome men.

1384
01:06:38.583 --> 01:06:41.250
After all of that. you still love her?

1385
01:06:42.917 --> 01:06:44.517
I think there's a misunderstanding here.

1386
01:06:45.167 --> 01:06:49.125
<i>I came on the show to tell my story.
not to badmouth my wife.</i>

1387
01:06:49.208 --> 01:06:51.417
<i>I hope that through this episode.</i>

1388
01:06:51.500 --> 01:06:53.083
<i>hopefully my wife will see it.</i>

1389
01:06:53.167 --> 01:06:55.625
<i>then she will understand my feelings.</i>

1390
01:06:55.708 --> 01:06:58.667
My wife is an extremely wonderful person.

1391
01:06:58.750 --> 01:06:59.792
She's the best!

1392
01:07:01.375 --> 01:07:02.292
Mr. Owl!

1393
01:07:02.375 --> 01:07:04.875
So is she "the best" or "the stress"?

1394
01:07:07.167 --> 01:07:09.875
I'm gonna be honest…

1395
01:07:10.792 --> 01:07:13.667
Back then. I was a total loser of a man.

1396
01:07:15.000 --> 01:07:16.125
Useless.

1397
01:07:16.208 --> 01:07:18.375
All day just playing games.

1398
01:07:18.458 --> 01:07:20.167
then friends dragged me to bars.

1399
01:07:20.250 --> 01:07:22.667
partying. blowing every last bit
of money there.

1400
01:07:22.750 --> 01:07:25.708
If my husband grows a beard.
he'd look similar to this.

1401
01:07:26.292 --> 01:07:28.500
But he wouldn't dare
go on the show. Are you crazy?

1402
01:07:28.583 --> 01:07:31.542
Just a vicious circle.
In general. I had no future.

1403
01:07:32.083 --> 01:07:33.833
It wasn't until I met my wife

1404
01:07:33.917 --> 01:07:35.667
that I truly understood

1405
01:07:35.750 --> 01:07:38.125
what it meant to live as a real person.

1406
01:07:38.958 --> 01:07:40.708
I swear to everyone…

1407
01:07:41.417 --> 01:07:45.458
I have never met anyone
as cool as my wife.

1408
01:07:46.125 --> 01:07:47.583
She goes to work…

1409
01:07:47.667 --> 01:07:48.684
Don't be mad for no reason.

1410
01:07:48.708 --> 01:07:50.708
<i>Solves all the problems there.</i>

1411
01:07:51.292 --> 01:07:52.500
<i>And when she's home.</i>

1412
01:07:52.583 --> 01:07:54.750
<i>she takes amazing care of me and our child</i>

1413
01:07:55.458 --> 01:07:57.542
- <i>and never complains.</i>
- Mr. Duc closes the deal!

1414
01:07:58.167 --> 01:07:59.167
Isn't she amazing?

1415
01:08:00.542 --> 01:08:02.542
Being with her. I learned many things.

1416
01:08:03.042 --> 01:08:04.042
I want to make money.

1417
01:08:04.875 --> 01:08:05.958
I want to work.

1418
01:08:06.458 --> 01:08:08.250
I want to better myself.

1419
01:08:08.333 --> 01:08:09.708
make her proud.

1420
01:08:11.500 --> 01:08:12.750
But Shoulder Sister.

1421
01:08:13.875 --> 01:08:15.542
isn't it true that most guys

1422
01:08:15.625 --> 01:08:19.458
usually want to… cover up for their woman?

1423
01:08:19.542 --> 01:08:21.208
Um… Just "cover" or "protect"?

1424
01:08:22.208 --> 01:08:23.708
Cover up?!?

1425
01:08:23.792 --> 01:08:24.917
Like his wife is a criminal?

1426
01:08:26.042 --> 01:08:27.833
Oh. protect. Protect.

1427
01:08:27.917 --> 01:08:28.917
Yeah. that.

1428
01:08:29.417 --> 01:08:32.708
I. on the other hand.
I want to be small next to my wife.

1429
01:08:33.833 --> 01:08:37.500
Well. drop your wife then. come
be small next to me. I'll protect you.

1430
01:08:37.583 --> 01:08:41.042
You think you can handle him?
Or you gonna lose your breath under him?

1431
01:08:41.125 --> 01:08:43.000
Oh my gosh. I can take it all.

1432
01:08:43.083 --> 01:08:45.292
Yeah right. you remind me of Bunnie.

1433
01:08:46.083 --> 01:08:47.375
Watch your damn mouth!

1434
01:08:47.458 --> 01:08:50.708
I know that no matter how hard I try.

1435
01:08:50.792 --> 01:08:53.167
I can never be as good as my wife.

1436
01:08:53.250 --> 01:08:55.292
So that's it. I'll step back.

1437
01:08:55.375 --> 01:08:57.042
I can back up and take care of her.

1438
01:08:59.042 --> 01:09:02.167
From everything you've told me.
you sound so genuine and heartfelt.

1439
01:09:02.250 --> 01:09:05.375
Why don' you just speak these words
to your wife directly?

1440
01:09:06.083 --> 01:09:08.000
<i>I believe any woman.
no matter how tough she is.</i>

1441
01:09:08.083 --> 01:09:11.208
<i>would be moved by words like these
from her own husband.</i>

1442
01:09:14.292 --> 01:09:15.625
Because at home.

1443
01:09:16.250 --> 01:09:18.208
no matter what I say.

1444
01:09:18.917 --> 01:09:22.292
she will always pick and choose
what she wants to hear.

1445
01:09:23.125 --> 01:09:25.875
<i>My wife is usually the most loving
and sentimental person.</i>

1446
01:09:25.958 --> 01:09:28.199
<i>but once jealousy kicks in.
she turns totally irrational.</i>

1447
01:09:28.833 --> 01:09:32.208
So. everything you've told me so far. do
you mean it from the bottom of your heart?

1448
01:09:33.917 --> 01:09:35.042
Actually…

1449
01:09:35.625 --> 01:09:38.167
My wife and I
have been separated for a month.

1450
01:09:38.792 --> 01:09:39.958
What a coincidence.

1451
01:09:40.042 --> 01:09:44.500
If I were a dishonest man.
I would've left quietly.

1452
01:09:44.583 --> 01:09:47.958
Why would I go on your show
and tell you this?

1453
01:09:48.042 --> 01:09:49.583
Don't you agree. Hai Ian?

1454
01:09:49.667 --> 01:09:50.958
Uh. Hai Linh.

1455
01:09:52.292 --> 01:09:53.375
Hai Ian?

1456
01:09:53.458 --> 01:09:55.292
<i>Okay. now…</i>

1457
01:09:55.375 --> 01:09:56.583
<i>Uh. Mr. Owl…</i>

1458
01:09:57.208 --> 01:09:58.792
In front of you is a camera.

1459
01:09:59.333 --> 01:10:01.458
Look straight at it.

1460
01:10:01.542 --> 01:10:03.625
Imagine that's your wife.

1461
01:10:04.333 --> 01:10:06.375
Do you have anything you want to tell her?

1462
01:10:06.458 --> 01:10:08.375
- Turn it up.
- Turn it up!

1463
01:10:08.458 --> 01:10:10.542
<i>I can't. Linh. that's too much for me.</i>

1464
01:10:10.625 --> 01:10:13.625
<i>- I can't do it.
- So what are you doing on this show?</i>

1465
01:10:14.125 --> 01:10:16.166
<i>Isn't it because you want
your wife to hear you out?</i>

1466
01:10:16.208 --> 01:10:20.208
Say whatever is on your mind.
No one will cut you off here.

1467
01:10:20.292 --> 01:10:22.042
I think she wants to hear it too.

1468
01:10:30.458 --> 01:10:31.708
<i>Ian…</i>

1469
01:10:37.125 --> 01:10:38.333
I miss Ben.

1470
01:10:42.250 --> 01:10:43.250
I miss you too.

1471
01:10:45.500 --> 01:10:46.875
<i>It's been a month.</i>

1472
01:10:47.958 --> 01:10:50.833
<i>I'm exhausted. Let's talk. honey.</i>

1473
01:10:52.208 --> 01:10:53.250
Is that okay?

1474
01:10:54.000 --> 01:10:56.000
<i>I can't stand it anymore.</i>

1475
01:10:58.333 --> 01:11:00.125
<i>I know I'm a total idiot</i>

1476
01:11:00.208 --> 01:11:02.042
<i>who always drives you crazy.</i>

1477
01:11:02.833 --> 01:11:04.000
But I swear to you.

1478
01:11:04.625 --> 01:11:06.458
there's no third woman. no side chick.

1479
01:11:06.542 --> 01:11:08.333
<i>I only love you. just you.</i>

1480
01:11:10.125 --> 01:11:11.667
I'll give you a family.

1481
01:11:12.333 --> 01:11:13.625
I'll make you happy.

1482
01:11:14.500 --> 01:11:16.708
<i>Because you're not an oldie.</i>

1483
01:11:16.792 --> 01:11:18.625
<i>you're my old but gold.</i>

1484
01:11:27.000 --> 01:11:29.333
- If it were me. I'd call right away.
- Obviously!

1485
01:11:29.917 --> 01:11:32.958
Call him. Maybe you'll get lucky tonight.

1486
01:11:33.042 --> 01:11:34.792
Stop playing hard to get.

1487
01:11:36.833 --> 01:11:38.417
- Call him.
- Call!

1488
01:11:38.500 --> 01:11:39.583
Oh. are you crazy?

1489
01:11:40.875 --> 01:11:41.875
Damn you.

1490
01:11:42.542 --> 01:11:44.375
So stubborn!

1491
01:11:44.458 --> 01:11:46.643
- Why is she like that?
- Just call him if she misses him.

1492
01:11:46.667 --> 01:11:48.476
She's going insane
but still playing tough. Poor girl!

1493
01:11:48.500 --> 01:11:50.208
Here. let me call him.

1494
01:11:50.292 --> 01:11:52.125
- Are you crazy?
- What are you gonna say?

1495
01:11:55.625 --> 01:11:57.583
That's a wrap for today.
Thank you. everyone.

1496
01:11:57.667 --> 01:11:58.875
Thank you. Mr. Owl.

1497
01:11:59.792 --> 01:12:01.917
Assist our guest. please. everyone.

1498
01:12:21.667 --> 01:12:22.708
Brother-in-law.

1499
01:12:26.542 --> 01:12:27.708
I'm sorry.

1500
01:12:29.958 --> 01:12:32.042
I've always had a bad attitude
towards you.

1501
01:12:32.125 --> 01:12:33.333
Really?

1502
01:12:34.292 --> 01:12:35.500
I didn't know.

1503
01:12:37.000 --> 01:12:38.833
It's okay. I…

1504
01:12:38.917 --> 01:12:41.000
I don't care about these things anyway.

1505
01:12:41.083 --> 01:12:43.667
I believe Ian will sympathize with you.

1506
01:12:43.750 --> 01:12:46.500
I stood there listening
and almost teared up a few times.

1507
01:12:46.583 --> 01:12:47.667
Stay out of it!

1508
01:12:47.750 --> 01:12:50.208
I mean. I said it just to put his mind
at ease. you know?

1509
01:12:52.625 --> 01:12:53.958
Take it!

1510
01:12:57.167 --> 01:12:58.542
<i>Tran Ngoc Son!</i>

1511
01:12:59.167 --> 01:13:00.458
<i>You go home right now.</i>

1512
01:13:02.417 --> 01:13:05.000
<i>How dare you go on TV
and badmouth me like this?</i>

1513
01:13:06.542 --> 01:13:08.917
If there's something to say.
say it at home.

1514
01:13:09.625 --> 01:13:11.667
You said you miss me

1515
01:13:11.750 --> 01:13:14.792
<i>and our daughter.
yet you wouldn't come home?</i>

1516
01:13:15.875 --> 01:13:18.958
<i>Come home and give Ben a bath.
She just wants her daddy.</i>

1517
01:13:19.792 --> 01:13:21.250
<i>Go home immediately.</i>

1518
01:13:21.333 --> 01:13:23.042
This is your last chance.

1519
01:14:06.375 --> 01:14:08.167
Hey. take this.

1520
01:14:08.250 --> 01:14:10.500
- What is this?
- It's a peace charm.

1521
01:14:10.583 --> 01:14:11.583
Very effective.

1522
01:14:11.667 --> 01:14:13.625
Put it in Son's pillow for him to lie on.

1523
01:14:13.708 --> 01:14:16.042
When he wakes up.
give it back to me. okay?

1524
01:14:16.125 --> 01:14:16.958
Thank you.

1525
01:14:17.042 --> 01:14:19.000
Hey. Ian. I have
three feng shui bracelets.

1526
01:14:19.083 --> 01:14:21.250
This is for you. and put this on Son.

1527
01:14:21.333 --> 01:14:24.167
May Heavens bless the illness away.

1528
01:14:24.250 --> 01:14:25.976
- Thank you very much.
- Don't forget about me.

1529
01:14:26.000 --> 01:14:27.792
I have something too.

1530
01:14:28.458 --> 01:14:30.375
Here. Take this.

1531
01:14:30.458 --> 01:14:32.458
Use on Son's lips to prevent dryness.

1532
01:14:33.042 --> 01:14:34.958
Patients with chapped lips look terrible.

1533
01:14:36.042 --> 01:14:38.292
Hey. don't get the wrong idea.
Me caring about him

1534
01:14:38.375 --> 01:14:41.083
doesn't mean I'm messing around
with your husband. okay?

1535
01:14:41.167 --> 01:14:43.125
He's just really pitiful.

1536
01:14:43.208 --> 01:14:46.125
- You keep yelling at him.
- I never yell at him. right?

1537
01:14:46.208 --> 01:14:48.542
- Yeah. you do. You just don't remember.
- All the time.

1538
01:14:48.625 --> 01:14:49.917
Listen to me.

1539
01:14:50.000 --> 01:14:52.583
If there's anything in here
you can't handle.

1540
01:14:52.667 --> 01:14:55.083
just call me.
I'll sort everything out. okay?

1541
01:14:55.167 --> 01:14:57.127
Remember. I know all the top doctors
in the field.

1542
01:14:57.875 --> 01:15:00.542
If you all leave me now. I'd die.

1543
01:15:00.625 --> 01:15:03.375
How can we ever leave you?

1544
01:15:03.458 --> 01:15:06.458
Mai. Ian. Cuc. Truc.
live and die together.

1545
01:15:06.542 --> 01:15:07.542
Come on.

1546
01:15:07.625 --> 01:15:08.833
Sisters for a day.

1547
01:15:08.917 --> 01:15:11.250
sisters forever.

1548
01:15:11.333 --> 01:15:13.917
Hey. hey. we're in a hospital!

1549
01:15:14.833 --> 01:15:16.250
I have to go.

1550
01:15:16.333 --> 01:15:17.792
Call me if you need anything.

1551
01:15:17.875 --> 01:15:19.208
You're so charming.

1552
01:15:20.042 --> 01:15:21.292
- Oh. Linh?
- Yes.

1553
01:15:21.375 --> 01:15:22.583
Take care of your sister.

1554
01:15:22.667 --> 01:15:24.292
Bye. Thank you. everyone.

1555
01:15:24.375 --> 01:15:26.296
- Cuc talks the loudest.
- You talk more than I do.

1556
01:15:26.375 --> 01:15:27.375
Don't even deny it.

1557
01:15:27.417 --> 01:15:29.351
- Just admit you're the loudmouth.
- Alright. stop blaming others.

1558
01:15:29.375 --> 01:15:30.958
So loud and noisy. but they love me.

1559
01:15:32.667 --> 01:15:33.750
Here you go.

1560
01:15:35.125 --> 01:15:36.667
This too. Burger.

1561
01:15:36.750 --> 01:15:38.417
- I don't want to eat.
- Eat up!

1562
01:15:38.500 --> 01:15:40.000
One person in the ER is enough.

1563
01:15:40.083 --> 01:15:41.809
- I don't need you in there too.
- I'm not hungry.

1564
01:15:41.833 --> 01:15:43.513
Just have some. even if you're not hungry.

1565
01:15:44.667 --> 01:15:45.833
Your phone's ringing.

1566
01:15:46.708 --> 01:15:48.875
No. it's my alarm to take the pills.

1567
01:15:48.958 --> 01:15:50.000
Are you sick?

1568
01:15:51.292 --> 01:15:53.208
It's for Son's blood pressure pills.

1569
01:15:53.292 --> 01:15:54.833
These days away from home.

1570
01:15:54.917 --> 01:15:57.601
the idiot forgot to take his medicine.
'cause I wasn't around to remind him.

1571
01:15:57.625 --> 01:15:59.208
so now he's here.

1572
01:16:00.417 --> 01:16:01.792
You and him are a pack now?

1573
01:16:01.875 --> 01:16:03.625
Gang up and badmouth me on your show?

1574
01:16:03.708 --> 01:16:05.268
I didn't know. He showed up by himself.

1575
01:16:05.792 --> 01:16:07.667
When I knew it was him. I was shocked too.

1576
01:16:07.750 --> 01:16:08.750
Right. so shocking!

1577
01:16:09.875 --> 01:16:11.917
It was the first time
I heard him talk like that.

1578
01:16:12.500 --> 01:16:14.292
and I just know he loves you for real.

1579
01:16:14.375 --> 01:16:15.750
Then suddenly I felt guilty.

1580
01:16:16.792 --> 01:16:18.708
I've been judging him badly all along.

1581
01:16:18.792 --> 01:16:20.792
When don't you assume the worst
about our marriage?

1582
01:16:20.833 --> 01:16:22.417
Both of us.

1583
01:16:23.000 --> 01:16:24.083
But was I wrong?

1584
01:16:27.625 --> 01:16:29.250
Well…

1585
01:16:29.333 --> 01:16:31.167
<i>Shoulder Sister</i> show.

1586
01:16:31.250 --> 01:16:32.417
with Hai Ian as the guest.

1587
01:16:32.500 --> 01:16:34.125
wanna hear my story?

1588
01:16:34.208 --> 01:16:35.792
I'll tell you everything.

1589
01:16:39.708 --> 01:16:41.417
Ben is not Son's daughter.

1590
01:16:45.958 --> 01:16:47.417
What the heck?

1591
01:16:47.500 --> 01:16:48.667
She's Tu's.

1592
01:16:49.792 --> 01:16:51.083
What are you saying?

1593
01:16:51.667 --> 01:16:52.667
Really?

1594
01:16:53.542 --> 01:16:54.942
Why have you never talked about it?

1595
01:16:55.958 --> 01:16:57.708
It's nothing to be proud of.

1596
01:16:57.792 --> 01:17:00.542
Remember when I was planning my wedding?

1597
01:17:01.167 --> 01:17:02.625
I was pregnant then.

1598
01:17:04.208 --> 01:17:06.000
Then I found out

1599
01:17:06.083 --> 01:17:08.333
that he has a wife and a kid already.

1600
01:17:08.417 --> 01:17:09.625
Isn't it great?

1601
01:17:10.167 --> 01:17:11.875
I can't believe how blind I've been.

1602
01:17:11.958 --> 01:17:14.639
My fiance had a side woman and a kid.
and I was completely clueless.

1603
01:17:16.167 --> 01:17:17.542
When we broke up.

1604
01:17:18.625 --> 01:17:20.167
I wanted to die.

1605
01:17:20.250 --> 01:17:21.625
Gosh. I was so dumb.

1606
01:17:24.958 --> 01:17:27.667
Right at that moment. Son came.

1607
01:17:27.750 --> 01:17:29.542
He was so in love with me.

1608
01:17:30.500 --> 01:17:32.875
I didn't accept him
because I hated his face.

1609
01:17:34.917 --> 01:17:37.042
Then he just kinda hung around.

1610
01:17:38.417 --> 01:17:40.083
He said…

1611
01:17:43.667 --> 01:17:45.250
"Let me marry you.

1612
01:17:46.208 --> 01:17:47.917
so your child has a father."

1613
01:18:02.500 --> 01:18:05.250
Being with me is a lot of pressure on him.

1614
01:18:08.167 --> 01:18:11.417
But I have no idea how to change myself.

1615
01:18:15.292 --> 01:18:17.167
I'm always afraid that one day.

1616
01:18:18.208 --> 01:18:21.250
there will be another woman out there.

1617
01:18:25.042 --> 01:18:28.167
I carried my fear from the ex to him.

1618
01:18:31.042 --> 01:18:33.125
I'm jealous like a crazy person.

1619
01:18:39.000 --> 01:18:40.625
Many times I feel like I'm insane…

1620
01:18:41.875 --> 01:18:43.208
But you are too!

1621
01:18:43.292 --> 01:18:44.333
What now?

1622
01:18:44.417 --> 01:18:47.577
If you hadn't stayed with me. I'd probably
never know how insane you really are.

1623
01:18:48.833 --> 01:18:51.042
You always insist on being right.

1624
01:18:51.125 --> 01:18:52.542
You are never wrong.

1625
01:18:53.083 --> 01:18:54.667
You really are an MC.

1626
01:18:56.083 --> 01:18:57.667
Why are you like a piece of wood?

1627
01:19:00.083 --> 01:19:02.167
Besides. you also refuse intimacy.

1628
01:19:02.750 --> 01:19:03.976
You don't give it to him. do you?

1629
01:19:04.000 --> 01:19:07.458
You have no idea. He's like a bull!

1630
01:19:08.208 --> 01:19:10.569
I get home. exhausted from work.
and he keeps asking for it.

1631
01:19:10.625 --> 01:19:11.750
You're saying no to a bull.

1632
01:19:11.833 --> 01:19:13.792
Have you seen my chicken?

1633
01:19:15.125 --> 01:19:17.417
When we started dating. Son and I

1634
01:19:17.500 --> 01:19:19.125
did it three times a day.

1635
01:19:19.208 --> 01:19:21.250
Now I'm lucky if I get one
every three weeks.

1636
01:19:21.333 --> 01:19:22.333
Maybe three months.

1637
01:19:23.958 --> 01:19:25.833
Sometimes I don't really understand.

1638
01:19:25.917 --> 01:19:27.792
Your husband is handsome.

1639
01:19:27.875 --> 01:19:30.042
successful. and makes a lot of money.

1640
01:19:30.125 --> 01:19:33.333
he loves you. cooks well. pampers you.

1641
01:19:33.417 --> 01:19:35.083
and you're still upset.

1642
01:19:36.250 --> 01:19:37.290
So what do you want. Linh?

1643
01:19:38.417 --> 01:19:39.893
I think it's because Mom spoiled you.

1644
01:19:39.917 --> 01:19:43.292
and I did too.
so you don't care about anyone.

1645
01:19:44.208 --> 01:19:47.083
Our mother was also in that
"never wrong" category.

1646
01:19:47.667 --> 01:19:50.083
So my dad and your dad checked out early.

1647
01:19:53.333 --> 01:19:54.833
Mom's genes are too strong.

1648
01:19:54.917 --> 01:19:57.083
making us both savages.

1649
01:19:57.167 --> 01:19:59.625
I'm ghetto savage. you're upscale savage.

1650
01:20:02.792 --> 01:20:04.083
Look at her!

1651
01:20:04.167 --> 01:20:06.583
Always a big smile!

1652
01:20:06.667 --> 01:20:07.792
I miss her!

1653
01:20:08.792 --> 01:20:11.583
So. do you remember
what she said before she passed?

1654
01:20:12.958 --> 01:20:15.208
You two try to live happily.

1655
01:20:16.917 --> 01:20:18.875
We're doing anything but that. yeah?

1656
01:20:25.625 --> 01:20:28.542
Okay… Go talk to your husband.

1657
01:20:28.625 --> 01:20:30.000
You can't wait too long.

1658
01:20:30.875 --> 01:20:34.208
A man is a predator hunting for its prey.

1659
01:20:34.292 --> 01:20:38.042
If you can't give him what he needs.
he'll have to find it from someone else.

1660
01:20:38.917 --> 01:20:41.125
Maybe he's just crushing on other girls.

1661
01:20:41.208 --> 01:20:43.458
You gave up before you even tried.

1662
01:20:43.542 --> 01:20:45.667
Does anyone really split
over one huge issue?

1663
01:20:45.750 --> 01:20:48.083
It's all the small things
that break couples.

1664
01:20:48.750 --> 01:20:50.208
Pointing fingers is simple.

1665
01:20:50.292 --> 01:20:51.833
Forgiveness is the tough part.

1666
01:20:52.750 --> 01:20:54.250
Rely on each other a bit.

1667
01:20:55.042 --> 01:20:57.750
That's the difference
between marriage and dating.

1668
01:20:59.333 --> 01:21:00.958
Life is so unpredictable.

1669
01:21:01.958 --> 01:21:05.542
How could I ever have imagined I'd still
be sitting here in the hospital right now.

1670
01:21:05.625 --> 01:21:07.125
sleepy as hell?

1671
01:21:13.083 --> 01:21:14.500
Mom had two husbands.

1672
01:21:15.250 --> 01:21:16.708
I did too.

1673
01:21:17.417 --> 01:21:19.042
Do you wanna join our team?

1674
01:21:42.333 --> 01:21:43.333
Come on.

1675
01:21:44.500 --> 01:21:47.167
It's okay. It's a good thing.

1676
01:21:49.583 --> 01:21:50.583
I love you. okay?

1677
01:21:53.250 --> 01:21:54.458
Why didn't you tell him?

1678
01:21:55.458 --> 01:21:58.250
- Ian!
- Wow. we only just mentioned you.

1679
01:21:58.333 --> 01:21:59.583
How is Son?

1680
01:22:00.250 --> 01:22:01.625
He's not critical anymore.

1681
01:22:01.708 --> 01:22:03.375
But how did you know we were here?

1682
01:22:03.458 --> 01:22:07.667
I stopped by the studio to visit Linh.
They told me. so I came right here.

1683
01:22:08.375 --> 01:22:09.542
Luckily. he's okay.

1684
01:22:17.000 --> 01:22:18.583
Hey. I won't change seats anymore.

1685
01:22:20.708 --> 01:22:22.583
Let's eat porridge. I brought some.

1686
01:22:22.667 --> 01:22:24.018
You've gotta have the strength
to take care of Son.

1687
01:22:24.042 --> 01:22:25.122
How many bowls did you buy?

1688
01:22:25.542 --> 01:22:26.667
Two.

1689
01:22:26.750 --> 01:22:28.500
But there are three of us here.

1690
01:22:28.583 --> 01:22:31.250
- I didn't know you'd be here.
- Right. I'm invisible.

1691
01:22:31.333 --> 01:22:32.333
Enough.

1692
01:22:34.250 --> 01:22:36.250
Now I see the truth in what people say.

1693
01:22:36.333 --> 01:22:40.042
Only your husband truly loves you.
Other men love their own women.

1694
01:22:40.125 --> 01:22:43.083
So go ahead and love each other.
I'm going back in to love my husband.

1695
01:22:43.167 --> 01:22:45.792
Gifted women like me
usually eat burgers alone.

1696
01:22:49.167 --> 01:22:50.167
Go away.

1697
01:22:51.208 --> 01:22:54.333
Have some porridge.
I just bought it. It's yummy.

1698
01:22:56.542 --> 01:22:57.958
Acting like you love me so much…

1699
01:22:58.542 --> 01:22:59.625
Of course I love you!

1700
01:23:02.125 --> 01:23:03.875
It smells so good. Wanna try some?

1701
01:23:05.958 --> 01:23:07.667
- Come on!
- Nope!

1702
01:23:07.750 --> 01:23:09.917
Eat so you have the strength to scold me.

1703
01:23:10.000 --> 01:23:11.500
Doesn't it smell good?

1704
01:23:17.375 --> 01:23:18.458
Where did you buy it?

1705
01:23:18.542 --> 01:23:20.167
- New place.
- Where?

1706
01:23:20.250 --> 01:23:21.458
Secret.

1707
01:23:21.542 --> 01:23:22.726
You went with Bunnie. didn't you?

1708
01:23:22.750 --> 01:23:24.042
There's no more Bunnie.

1709
01:23:24.125 --> 01:23:26.125
- Liar.
- Please don't be mad at me.

1710
01:23:26.208 --> 01:23:27.458
Please!

1711
01:23:42.292 --> 01:23:43.684
- What the hell?
- Linh. I don't know...

1712
01:23:43.708 --> 01:23:44.542
Are you kidding me?

1713
01:23:44.625 --> 01:23:46.393
- I swear to you. I don't know.
- Why is she here?

1714
01:23:46.417 --> 01:23:48.208
Linh. she's stalking me for sure.

1715
01:23:49.125 --> 01:23:51.250
Linh! Linh!

1716
01:23:52.583 --> 01:23:55.226
KIM. THIS IS PHONG. HA'S BOSS
SHE LOVES ME AND IS HARRASSING MY FAMILY

1717
01:23:55.250 --> 01:23:58.917
I KNOW YOUR PROBLEM IS JUST MONEY
I WILL HELP YOU AND HELP MYSELF

1718
01:23:59.000 --> 01:24:00.750
I HOPE YOU KNOW WHAT TO DO

1719
01:24:02.833 --> 01:24:04.333
HOW CAN I TRUST YOU?

1720
01:24:04.417 --> 01:24:07.875
HA LIVES AT 2F SUNSET TOWER IN D7
GO FIND HER. AND SEND ME YOUR BANK INFO

1721
01:24:30.333 --> 01:24:32.083
Are you crazy?

1722
01:24:32.167 --> 01:24:34.333
This is a hospital.
What are you doing? Huh?

1723
01:24:34.417 --> 01:24:36.934
You came here to destroy my family.
and only then would you be satisfied?

1724
01:24:36.958 --> 01:24:39.167
Tell me! What do you want?

1725
01:24:39.250 --> 01:24:40.625
I miss you.

1726
01:24:40.708 --> 01:24:41.875
I love you.

1727
01:24:41.958 --> 01:24:43.583
I haven't been okay for days.

1728
01:24:43.667 --> 01:24:45.292
Phong. don't leave me. I'd die!

1729
01:24:45.375 --> 01:24:48.708
You still love me. right?
Tell me! You love me!

1730
01:24:48.792 --> 01:24:50.750
Hey! Hey! Are you insane?

1731
01:24:50.833 --> 01:24:52.167
This is mental.

1732
01:24:52.250 --> 01:24:53.667
What are you doing?

1733
01:24:53.750 --> 01:24:55.042
How did you know I was here?

1734
01:24:55.125 --> 01:24:56.667
You're stalking me. aren't you?

1735
01:24:57.417 --> 01:24:58.958
I'm not stalking you.

1736
01:24:59.042 --> 01:25:01.333
I just wanted to find you.

1737
01:25:01.417 --> 01:25:02.833
You're scaring me.

1738
01:25:03.458 --> 01:25:05.208
I'm gonna tell you one last time.

1739
01:25:05.292 --> 01:25:06.833
Stay away from my family.

1740
01:25:06.917 --> 01:25:08.833
Don't touch my wife.

1741
01:25:08.917 --> 01:25:10.000
Or I'll call the police.

1742
01:25:20.292 --> 01:25:22.208
So you don't care about me anymore?

1743
01:25:22.292 --> 01:25:23.875
If that's the case.

1744
01:25:23.958 --> 01:25:27.625
I'll make sure the whole world
cares about us.

1745
01:25:29.708 --> 01:25:31.375
Only a few seconds…

1746
01:25:32.292 --> 01:25:34.167
The second I hit the ground.

1747
01:25:34.250 --> 01:25:36.290
everyone will be paying attention
to me then. Phong.

1748
01:25:36.875 --> 01:25:38.208
Are you threatening me?

1749
01:25:39.417 --> 01:25:40.417
Try me!

1750
01:25:43.042 --> 01:25:44.542
Asshole!

1751
01:25:45.250 --> 01:25:46.542
Phong!

1752
01:26:04.000 --> 01:26:08.042
TRAN KIM

1753
01:26:17.000 --> 01:26:18.708
BALANCE CHANGE +300.000.000

1754
01:26:22.583 --> 01:26:23.625
I GOT THE MONEY

1755
01:26:32.292 --> 01:26:35.583
How many more times do I have to tell you
I didn't go to the hospital with her?

1756
01:26:36.167 --> 01:26:37.417
Why won't you believe me?

1757
01:26:38.000 --> 01:26:39.708
I only believe what I see.

1758
01:26:40.833 --> 01:26:42.292
Do you think I'm a kid?

1759
01:26:42.375 --> 01:26:43.375
She loves you!

1760
01:26:43.458 --> 01:26:45.726
If you haven't done a thing.
why did she give you that look?

1761
01:26:45.750 --> 01:26:47.708
That's the look of someone
who's deeply in love.

1762
01:26:47.792 --> 01:26:49.875
There's also hatred in there.
I see it all.

1763
01:26:49.958 --> 01:26:51.750
Stop talking now. My head hurts.

1764
01:26:54.292 --> 01:26:55.625
Every fight is always the same.

1765
01:26:59.542 --> 01:27:02.292
If I were you. I'd choose to listen.

1766
01:27:02.375 --> 01:27:05.250
I'd want to hear their side
and hope it's all just a misunderstanding.

1767
01:27:05.333 --> 01:27:07.417
I don't want to believe
they've done me wrong.

1768
01:27:07.500 --> 01:27:08.500
What about you?

1769
01:27:08.583 --> 01:27:11.458
It feels like you just want people
to be at fault.

1770
01:27:11.542 --> 01:27:12.625
Why is that?

1771
01:27:13.208 --> 01:27:14.768
Give it a shot.
hear what they have to say.

1772
01:27:14.792 --> 01:27:18.292
If it doesn't register with you.
then you can get angry afterward. okay?

1773
01:27:18.375 --> 01:27:21.255
Why do you always jump to conclusions
before you even find out the truth?

1774
01:27:21.667 --> 01:27:24.250
Every little fight
and you immediately threaten divorce.

1775
01:27:25.458 --> 01:27:28.375
There are times when I wonder
if you still want to fight for us at all.

1776
01:27:31.500 --> 01:27:33.833
So you think I haven't tried at all?

1777
01:27:44.125 --> 01:27:46.500
Honestly. I've been really stressed
these past few days.

1778
01:27:47.667 --> 01:27:49.083
I've just been holding it together.

1779
01:27:51.250 --> 01:27:53.708
You know how much I hate
being betrayed. right?

1780
01:27:53.792 --> 01:27:56.875
To be honest. if I was still the old me.

1781
01:27:56.958 --> 01:27:59.458
just this alone would've made me
break up with you right away.

1782
01:27:59.542 --> 01:28:01.302
I wouldn't be sitting here
talking like this.

1783
01:28:02.042 --> 01:28:04.083
I would've hated you by now.

1784
01:28:06.792 --> 01:28:08.583
But I'm hating myself right now.

1785
01:28:10.167 --> 01:28:11.667
I hate Hai Linh.

1786
01:28:12.583 --> 01:28:14.542
I realized everything is because of her.

1787
01:28:15.125 --> 01:28:18.542
She acts like she's so wise.
always giving advice to everyone.

1788
01:28:18.625 --> 01:28:21.083
when she's actually the one
living the worst life.

1789
01:28:22.583 --> 01:28:25.000
Mom and Ian always control their husbands.

1790
01:28:25.083 --> 01:28:26.583
I don't want to live like that.

1791
01:28:26.667 --> 01:28:27.792
Can't you see?

1792
01:28:27.875 --> 01:28:31.458
You can go wherever. do whatever. be
with whoever. You're free to be yourself.

1793
01:28:32.167 --> 01:28:33.792
I don't even know your phone passcode.

1794
01:28:34.375 --> 01:28:36.375
I don't know how much money you make.

1795
01:28:36.458 --> 01:28:38.792
I don't even know your work schedule.

1796
01:28:42.208 --> 01:28:43.375
So much so that…

1797
01:28:43.458 --> 01:28:45.500
I don't even know that you're sad.

1798
01:28:50.458 --> 01:28:52.833
Truth is. if you hadn't called me out
straight to my face.

1799
01:28:52.917 --> 01:28:55.542
I wouldn't have known
how deeply I hurt you.

1800
01:28:59.875 --> 01:29:02.333
I keep thinking I'm the luckiest girl.

1801
01:29:02.417 --> 01:29:04.000
And I really am. don't you think?

1802
01:29:04.083 --> 01:29:05.792
I have a good job.

1803
01:29:05.875 --> 01:29:07.500
I'm successful.

1804
01:29:07.583 --> 01:29:09.333
Out there. everyone loves me.

1805
01:29:09.417 --> 01:29:11.333
At home. my family cherishes me.

1806
01:29:11.417 --> 01:29:12.917
I have a good husband.

1807
01:29:15.417 --> 01:29:16.875
But I'm a total idiot.

1808
01:29:18.542 --> 01:29:20.875
I only remembered I have a husband.

1809
01:29:23.375 --> 01:29:25.083
But I forgot…

1810
01:29:25.167 --> 01:29:27.250
My husband also needs a wife.

1811
01:29:31.458 --> 01:29:36.208
So if I've ever made you sad
or left you feeling lonely…

1812
01:29:39.333 --> 01:29:40.417
I'm sorry. okay?

1813
01:29:43.833 --> 01:29:46.750
All this time. I thought I wasn't afraid
of anything in this world.

1814
01:29:46.833 --> 01:29:50.042
But after what happened.
I realized I'm not fearless.

1815
01:29:52.833 --> 01:29:54.250
I'm afraid of losing you.

1816
01:30:39.500 --> 01:30:40.667
- Bunnie!
- Let go.

1817
01:30:40.750 --> 01:30:41.833
- Bunnie!
- I said let go.

1818
01:30:43.250 --> 01:30:45.750
- Bunnie! Listen to me!
- Let me go!

1819
01:30:47.292 --> 01:30:49.875
- Where were you?
- You stalked me all the way here?

1820
01:30:50.458 --> 01:30:52.500
No. I… I…

1821
01:30:53.917 --> 01:30:55.625
Why did you move here without telling me?

1822
01:30:55.708 --> 01:30:56.934
Why have you been hiding from me
for a whole month?

1823
01:30:56.958 --> 01:30:58.958
I have no reason to hide from you.

1824
01:30:59.042 --> 01:31:00.667
Who do you think you are?

1825
01:31:01.417 --> 01:31:03.083
What are you saying?

1826
01:31:03.167 --> 01:31:04.559
Where were you? Why are you soaked?

1827
01:31:04.583 --> 01:31:06.500
Why are you dressed like that?

1828
01:31:06.583 --> 01:31:07.750
Why are you so drunk?

1829
01:31:07.833 --> 01:31:08.917
I like it.

1830
01:31:09.500 --> 01:31:11.083
I like wearing clothes like this.

1831
01:31:11.167 --> 01:31:12.625
What?

1832
01:31:14.667 --> 01:31:15.708
Let go of me.

1833
01:31:15.792 --> 01:31:17.750
- I said let me go.
- Bunnie. listen to me. please.

1834
01:31:17.833 --> 01:31:21.625
- Get your hands off me.
- Listen to me. listen to me.

1835
01:31:21.708 --> 01:31:25.250
Today I came here with no intention
of causing trouble. no yelling. nothing.

1836
01:31:25.333 --> 01:31:27.208
I just want to tell you…

1837
01:31:30.208 --> 01:31:32.917
I've saved up the money.
Can we get married now?

1838
01:31:33.000 --> 01:31:34.583
You've got money?

1839
01:31:35.625 --> 01:31:39.208
You got money. Go find someone to marry.
Why do you keep hanging around me?

1840
01:31:39.292 --> 01:31:40.708
Aren't you tired?

1841
01:31:40.792 --> 01:31:42.750
'Cause I'm really tired.

1842
01:31:42.833 --> 01:31:44.542
I said I don't love you.

1843
01:31:44.625 --> 01:31:47.208
What's the point of chasing someone
who doesn't love you?

1844
01:31:47.292 --> 01:31:50.625
- Why are you talking like this?
- That's just me.

1845
01:31:50.708 --> 01:31:53.500
I like talking like this. So what?

1846
01:31:53.583 --> 01:31:55.101
Stop having a one-sided crush on him.
He doesn't love you.

1847
01:31:55.125 --> 01:31:57.125
Who told you it's one-sided?

1848
01:31:58.750 --> 01:32:01.792
Who said it's a one-sided love?

1849
01:32:04.500 --> 01:32:05.583
Phong!

1850
01:32:08.500 --> 01:32:09.917
Please tell me the truth.

1851
01:32:11.875 --> 01:32:13.395
Was there anything between you and Ha?

1852
01:32:15.417 --> 01:32:18.958
I promise I won't be angry
or make a fuss anymore.

1853
01:32:20.750 --> 01:32:24.375
No matter what happens. I will
accept it in the most positive way.

1854
01:32:26.208 --> 01:32:27.667
I only want to know the truth.

1855
01:32:30.042 --> 01:32:31.250
Tell me.

1856
01:32:46.333 --> 01:32:47.500
I'm sorry…

1857
01:32:50.042 --> 01:32:51.417
I was wrong.

1858
01:32:52.000 --> 01:32:55.333
I'm almost 30. I'm not a child. okay?

1859
01:32:55.417 --> 01:32:56.958
Listen carefully.

1860
01:32:58.375 --> 01:33:01.208
I slept with him.

1861
01:33:01.833 --> 01:33:04.042
<i>We've been dating for a whole month.</i>

1862
01:33:04.125 --> 01:33:06.833
<i>Now that he dumped me. are you happy?</i>

1863
01:33:08.667 --> 01:33:10.417
You know how I ended up like this?

1864
01:33:10.500 --> 01:33:11.792
It's all because of you!

1865
01:33:11.875 --> 01:33:13.875
You're the one who got me into this mess.

1866
01:33:13.958 --> 01:33:16.059
Where am I supposed to get 4k
right now to pay them back?

1867
01:33:16.083 --> 01:33:17.250
Why are you crying?

1868
01:33:17.333 --> 01:33:19.458
<i>You made me fall for him.</i>

1869
01:33:19.542 --> 01:33:20.958
You criticized me.

1870
01:33:21.042 --> 01:33:22.667
- You said "him"?
- <i>tormented me.</i>

1871
01:33:22.750 --> 01:33:25.208
<i>and because of you. I had to go
and beg him for help.</i>

1872
01:33:25.292 --> 01:33:27.542
<i>You made me a home wrecker.</i>

1873
01:33:27.625 --> 01:33:29.500
I'm here. She won't be yelling at anyone.

1874
01:33:29.583 --> 01:33:31.064
Call her if you have nothing to hide.

1875
01:33:31.125 --> 01:33:32.125
Fine.

1876
01:33:32.208 --> 01:33:35.208
<i>I tried so hard to keep living with you.</i>

1877
01:33:35.292 --> 01:33:37.292
<i>but you're the one
who forced me into this.</i>

1878
01:33:37.375 --> 01:33:40.250
<i>I didn't think you would
treat me so horribly.</i>

1879
01:33:40.333 --> 01:33:41.583
No need to follow him.

1880
01:33:41.667 --> 01:33:42.750
- Son!
- Phong!

1881
01:33:42.833 --> 01:33:44.375
Son. your phone.

1882
01:33:45.750 --> 01:33:47.833
<i>If you hadn't pushed me
to the absolute edge.</i>

1883
01:33:47.917 --> 01:33:50.833
<i>I might not have opened up
to him that night.</i>

1884
01:33:50.917 --> 01:33:53.542
<i>- You can live here from now on.
- I can't afford a house this big.</i>

1885
01:33:53.625 --> 01:33:54.833
Don't worry about it.

1886
01:33:54.917 --> 01:33:56.042
I can take care of you.

1887
01:33:56.125 --> 01:33:59.417
<i>With your blessing. I ended up with him.</i>

1888
01:33:59.500 --> 01:34:01.708
Because of you. my life
became this miserable.

1889
01:34:01.792 --> 01:34:04.500
Because of you. I became a home wrecker.
Are you satisfied now?

1890
01:34:04.583 --> 01:34:06.059
Don't say that.
You're just trying to provoke me.

1891
01:34:06.083 --> 01:34:08.083
Why the hell do I need to provoke you?

1892
01:34:08.167 --> 01:34:11.500
My life is already fucked up enough.
Stop messing with it.

1893
01:34:11.583 --> 01:34:13.542
The thing I regret most
is ever meeting you.

1894
01:34:13.625 --> 01:34:15.042
- I said enough.
- I hate you!

1895
01:34:15.125 --> 01:34:18.125
Even if he dumps me another hundred times.

1896
01:34:18.208 --> 01:34:20.083
- I'm never coming back to you.
- I said enough!

1897
01:34:20.167 --> 01:34:22.125
I said enough!
What the fuck are you saying?

1898
01:34:22.208 --> 01:34:23.292
You fucking love him?

1899
01:34:23.375 --> 01:34:25.500
If you're gonna kill me.
make sure I'm dead!

1900
01:34:25.583 --> 01:34:28.458
- How dare you?
- If I survive. I will never be with you.

1901
01:34:28.542 --> 01:34:30.250
Hey! Stop!

1902
01:34:30.333 --> 01:34:31.542
What are you saying?

1903
01:34:32.667 --> 01:34:33.583
Where do you live?

1904
01:34:33.667 --> 01:34:34.875
Which apartment?

1905
01:34:34.958 --> 01:34:36.351
- I live here.
- What are you talking about?

1906
01:34:36.375 --> 01:34:37.583
Why do you do that?

1907
01:34:37.667 --> 01:34:40.208
- Say it!
- I said I don't fucking love you!

1908
01:34:40.292 --> 01:34:43.042
You are an asshole!
Get the fuck out of my life!

1909
01:34:43.125 --> 01:34:44.167
Fuck off!

1910
01:34:45.542 --> 01:34:47.958
Let go! Let go!

1911
01:34:48.042 --> 01:34:49.958
Bunnie! The fuck did you just say?

1912
01:34:50.042 --> 01:34:52.208
Bunnie! Bunnie!

1913
01:34:54.083 --> 01:34:56.500
Get to Area 2F now.
Someone's causing trouble here.

1914
01:34:56.583 --> 01:34:57.833
Call for backup.

1915
01:35:01.667 --> 01:35:03.500
It's okay. Don't cry.

1916
01:35:03.583 --> 01:35:05.250
Tell me. Phong.

1917
01:35:10.000 --> 01:35:11.333
I…

1918
01:35:16.708 --> 01:35:19.708
Back when we first got together.
everything was simple.

1919
01:35:20.625 --> 01:35:22.458
During the day. we both went to work.

1920
01:35:22.542 --> 01:35:26.083
and at night. we'd tell each other
about our long day.

1921
01:35:26.167 --> 01:35:28.083
On weekends. I'd take you out.

1922
01:35:28.167 --> 01:35:30.083
We did so many things together.

1923
01:35:31.208 --> 01:35:32.667
And then…

1924
01:35:36.792 --> 01:35:38.250
Your career got better.

1925
01:35:40.125 --> 01:35:42.750
You became more successful. more famous.

1926
01:35:43.667 --> 01:35:45.167
You worked more.

1927
01:35:46.875 --> 01:35:48.958
You had less time for me.

1928
01:35:51.167 --> 01:35:53.125
And sometimes I just…

1929
01:35:54.542 --> 01:35:56.042
Felt really lost.

1930
01:35:59.250 --> 01:36:02.042
And somehow. a distance grew between us.

1931
01:36:02.875 --> 01:36:04.750
And then. when I was…

1932
01:36:04.833 --> 01:36:07.750
At my loneliest. I met Ha.

1933
01:36:09.125 --> 01:36:11.458
I related to her because

1934
01:36:11.542 --> 01:36:14.000
she was struggling in love too.

1935
01:36:14.917 --> 01:36:16.917
I don't even know what came over me.

1936
01:36:18.042 --> 01:36:19.667
I just suddenly wanted to protect her…

1937
01:36:22.750 --> 01:36:24.000
Maybe…

1938
01:36:27.583 --> 01:36:28.875
Maybe because…

1939
01:36:28.958 --> 01:36:30.292
I was craving love.

1940
01:36:40.833 --> 01:36:43.750
Just because I made you sad.
you had to hurt me back?

1941
01:36:43.833 --> 01:36:46.583
- I was wrong…
- If I was wrong. you should've told me!

1942
01:36:46.667 --> 01:36:48.792
Why did you treat me like that?

1943
01:36:48.875 --> 01:36:52.417
What am I supposed to do now?
I don't know anything anymore.

1944
01:36:52.500 --> 01:36:55.292
Give me back the the Phong I loved.

1945
01:36:56.917 --> 01:37:01.125
<i>Back then. I thought it was just
a moment of emotion between me and Ha.</i>

1946
01:37:01.208 --> 01:37:02.083
Yes!

1947
01:37:02.167 --> 01:37:05.042
<i>Then. when it ended.
I'd help her financially.</i>

1948
01:37:05.125 --> 01:37:07.309
You can stay in that apartment.
I'll cover two years of rent.

1949
01:37:07.333 --> 01:37:09.917
I wouldn't let this affect our family.

1950
01:37:10.500 --> 01:37:11.542
I never thought that…

1951
01:37:11.625 --> 01:37:13.542
I didn't date you for money.

1952
01:37:14.042 --> 01:37:15.375
I love you.

1953
01:37:15.458 --> 01:37:18.875
Is it because she's the chairman's sister
that you're conflicted?

1954
01:37:18.958 --> 01:37:20.143
I know you have your own struggles.

1955
01:37:20.167 --> 01:37:21.726
- Calm down. Bunnie.
- I just need you to say you love me.

1956
01:37:21.750 --> 01:37:23.559
- Just say you won't leave me.
- I told you. this is the office...

1957
01:37:23.583 --> 01:37:25.500
- Promise me!
- I can't promise you anything.

1958
01:37:25.583 --> 01:37:27.417
- I can wait for you.
- Honey!

1959
01:37:29.792 --> 01:37:31.542
I'm sorry. sweetie.

1960
01:37:33.917 --> 01:37:37.083
No matter what decision
you make now. I'll accept it.

1961
01:37:37.875 --> 01:37:38.958
But…

1962
01:37:41.542 --> 01:37:43.708
I just wanted to be honest with you.

1963
01:37:45.583 --> 01:37:47.625
I don't want to lie anymore.

1964
01:37:49.500 --> 01:37:50.917
Tell me the truth now.

1965
01:37:53.208 --> 01:37:54.667
Do you still love me?

1966
01:37:57.083 --> 01:37:58.458
Why would you ask that?

1967
01:38:01.542 --> 01:38:03.500
I only want to love you.

1968
01:38:07.458 --> 01:38:09.542
I said I didn't want to be like Ian.

1969
01:38:09.625 --> 01:38:11.625
But I know I'm exactly like her.

1970
01:38:13.542 --> 01:38:18.750
So even if I forgive you now.
I'll still torture both of us later.

1971
01:38:19.458 --> 01:38:20.792
I don't want that.

1972
01:38:25.333 --> 01:38:26.958
Give me one night.

1973
01:38:28.458 --> 01:38:30.375
Tonight. I want to think carefully.

1974
01:38:31.583 --> 01:38:33.667
I want to make the right decision.

1975
01:38:36.667 --> 01:38:38.875
I want to talk to myself and see…

1976
01:38:40.292 --> 01:38:42.042
If I can forgive you.

1977
01:38:48.542 --> 01:38:49.625
Thank you.

1978
01:38:53.292 --> 01:38:55.167
Thank you for listening to me.

1979
01:38:57.917 --> 01:38:59.458
I'm sorry.

1980
01:39:55.375 --> 01:39:56.667
<i>Does your head still hurt?</i>

1981
01:39:58.833 --> 01:40:00.042
<i>I'm feeling better now.</i>

1982
01:40:00.958 --> 01:40:01.875
Don't worry.

1983
01:40:01.958 --> 01:40:03.958
I'm here with you. No one can bother you.

1984
01:40:05.542 --> 01:40:07.042
<i>I'd rather go to work and see you</i>

1985
01:40:07.125 --> 01:40:09.125
<i>than stay home on my day off
with nothing to do.</i>

1986
01:40:10.042 --> 01:40:11.417
Bunnie!

1987
01:40:11.500 --> 01:40:13.083
I missed you so much!

1988
01:40:14.125 --> 01:40:16.583
<i>I just want to see
you looking beautiful. smiling.</i>

1989
01:40:16.667 --> 01:40:17.667
<i>being happy.</i>

1990
01:40:21.000 --> 01:40:22.958
Wow. you can actually cook?

1991
01:40:24.000 --> 01:40:26.041
If you know good food.
you have to know how to cook.

1992
01:40:38.333 --> 01:40:41.083
What did I ever do to you
for you to treat me like this?

1993
01:40:41.167 --> 01:40:43.833
You made me fall for you.
and now you're hiding from me?

1994
01:40:43.917 --> 01:40:46.833
You're a bastard! You're scared everyone
will find out. aren't you?

1995
01:40:46.917 --> 01:40:48.083
<i>Bunnie!</i>

1996
01:40:48.667 --> 01:40:49.917
<i>From now on. this is your home.</i>

1997
01:40:52.750 --> 01:40:54.958
<i>I'm here now. No one will bother you.</i>

1998
01:40:55.667 --> 01:40:58.107
<i>Thank you for your contributions
to the company all this time.</i>

1999
01:40:58.417 --> 01:41:00.708
<i>How much money do you want to end this?</i>

2000
01:41:01.667 --> 01:41:04.458
- I truly love you!
- But I don't love you anymore.

2001
01:41:04.542 --> 01:41:05.542
Do you understand?

2002
01:41:06.000 --> 01:41:07.917
Don't touch my wife.

2003
01:41:08.000 --> 01:41:09.500
Or I'll call the police.

2004
01:42:06.750 --> 01:42:07.750
<i>Bunnie!</i>

2005
01:42:08.708 --> 01:42:10.750
- <i>You...</i>
- So you finally decided to call me?

2006
01:42:12.125 --> 01:42:15.167
I know that no matter what I say now.
I've already hurt you.

2007
01:42:16.375 --> 01:42:18.250
I admit I treated you terribly.

2008
01:42:19.208 --> 01:42:22.250
So if there's anything
you want to ask. go ahead.

2009
01:42:23.208 --> 01:42:24.625
I won't run away anymore.

2010
01:42:26.333 --> 01:42:28.375
<i>I promise I'll answer honestly.</i>

2011
01:42:28.458 --> 01:42:29.458
Okay. tell me.

2012
01:42:30.042 --> 01:42:33.125
<i>We were happy. Why did you wanna break up?</i>

2013
01:42:33.208 --> 01:42:34.875
Back then. you really confused me.

2014
01:42:34.958 --> 01:42:37.250
<i>I didn't understand why
you fell for me so fast.</i>

2015
01:42:37.333 --> 01:42:38.684
Where did you go the past few days?

2016
01:42:38.708 --> 01:42:41.250
I'm your secretary. I know your schedule.

2017
01:42:41.333 --> 01:42:42.792
You weren't busy with anything.

2018
01:42:42.875 --> 01:42:44.875
What did I do wrong
that made you avoid me?

2019
01:42:44.958 --> 01:42:47.542
- Why did you treat me like that?
- Bunnie!

2020
01:42:47.625 --> 01:42:49.184
I feel like you're starting to control me.

2021
01:42:49.208 --> 01:42:51.417
- I'm not controlling you.
- You are.

2022
01:42:51.500 --> 01:42:53.833
You called me dozens of times in a row.

2023
01:42:53.917 --> 01:42:55.059
Because I missed you so much.

2024
01:42:55.083 --> 01:42:56.333
That's not normal missing.

2025
01:42:57.500 --> 01:42:58.667
And there's something else.

2026
01:42:58.750 --> 01:43:00.250
Why did you go on my wife's show?

2027
01:43:00.833 --> 01:43:01.893
<i>What were you trying to prove there?</i>

2028
01:43:01.917 --> 01:43:03.000
<i>If you weren't happy.</i>

2029
01:43:03.083 --> 01:43:04.542
<i>would you leave your husband?</i>

2030
01:43:05.542 --> 01:43:06.851
<i>You were attacking her. you know that?</i>

2031
01:43:06.875 --> 01:43:09.583
I just wanted to show you
that Linh is strong enough

2032
01:43:09.667 --> 01:43:11.708
to accept that.

2033
01:43:11.792 --> 01:43:13.458
You're scaring me. Bunnie.

2034
01:43:13.542 --> 01:43:15.042
<i>What did I tell you?</i>

2035
01:43:15.125 --> 01:43:17.292
<i>Don't call me after 9 p.m.</i>

2036
01:43:17.375 --> 01:43:18.875
<i>That's when I'm with my wife.</i>

2037
01:43:18.958 --> 01:43:21.042
<i>We were dating.
but she did nothing wrong to us.</i>

2038
01:43:21.125 --> 01:43:23.042
So you made me the bad guy?

2039
01:43:23.125 --> 01:43:25.125
We'd only been together for a month.

2040
01:43:25.208 --> 01:43:27.625
<i>But I felt like. little by little.
you were losing control.</i>

2041
01:43:27.708 --> 01:43:30.292
<i>I missed you.
You're dumping me. aren't you?</i>

2042
01:43:30.375 --> 01:43:31.708
How can you be so cruel to me?

2043
01:43:31.792 --> 01:43:33.226
My family's here. What are you doing?

2044
01:43:33.250 --> 01:43:35.417
<i>I didn't know
what you might do next. Bunnie…</i>

2045
01:43:36.000 --> 01:43:38.125
<i>I really need this family.</i>

2046
01:43:38.792 --> 01:43:40.250
I can't lose my wife.

2047
01:43:41.250 --> 01:43:45.417
Every sentence. it's "my wife. my wife".
So you still love her that much. huh?

2048
01:43:45.500 --> 01:43:46.542
<i>I'll give you some money.</i>

2049
01:43:46.625 --> 01:43:49.833
so you can live without worrying anymore.

2050
01:43:50.417 --> 01:43:53.125
<i>This is something I want to do
to make it up to you.</i>

2051
01:43:53.792 --> 01:43:55.542
<i>I'll give you 40 grand.</i>

2052
01:43:56.167 --> 01:43:57.500
<i>Let's end this.</i>

2053
01:43:59.042 --> 01:44:00.792
I'm truly sorry.

2054
01:44:01.750 --> 01:44:03.292
<i>If that's your offer. then fine.</i>

2055
01:44:04.875 --> 01:44:06.792
Just give me the money
and be done with it.

2056
01:44:07.417 --> 01:44:09.000
Thank you for understanding me.

2057
01:44:11.083 --> 01:44:12.500
<i>I'm sorry. Bunnie.</i>

2058
01:44:52.667 --> 01:44:53.667
Honey.

2059
01:44:54.542 --> 01:44:56.000
I made breakfast.

2060
01:44:56.083 --> 01:44:57.375
Come down and eat with me.

2061
01:45:00.292 --> 01:45:01.667
Let's skip breakfast.

2062
01:45:02.375 --> 01:45:03.833
Can we talk first?

2063
01:45:08.083 --> 01:45:09.417
You're my husband. I know you.

2064
01:45:10.042 --> 01:45:11.375
I know you're a romantic person.

2065
01:45:12.125 --> 01:45:13.292
Very emotional.

2066
01:45:14.083 --> 01:45:16.500
So your need to be loved is stronger too.

2067
01:45:16.583 --> 01:45:17.625
I know.

2068
01:45:18.792 --> 01:45:20.792
While I'm too dry.

2069
01:45:21.333 --> 01:45:23.667
I don't pay attention
to your feelings at all.

2070
01:45:23.750 --> 01:45:25.792
Sometimes I even snap at you.

2071
01:45:26.500 --> 01:45:29.167
So what you did. I…

2072
01:45:29.917 --> 01:45:31.292
I understand it too.

2073
01:45:32.417 --> 01:45:35.375
I know I'm partly at fault as well.

2074
01:45:37.833 --> 01:45:41.083
So. you know. when you were
honest with me yesterday…

2075
01:45:41.917 --> 01:45:44.250
To be honest…

2076
01:45:45.500 --> 01:45:47.708
Deep down.
I already wanted to forgive you.

2077
01:45:49.833 --> 01:45:50.833
Thank you.

2078
01:45:51.917 --> 01:45:54.417
I promise. from now on.
I won't hurt you anymore.

2079
01:45:54.500 --> 01:45:55.625
I…

2080
01:45:56.375 --> 01:45:58.125
I think I'll forgive you.

2081
01:46:00.833 --> 01:46:03.458
- Let's get breakfast.
- If you weren't such a bastard.

2082
01:46:06.292 --> 01:46:08.750
Oh. keep your shoes on. Keep them on.

2083
01:46:09.542 --> 01:46:10.542
She's here.

2084
01:46:27.292 --> 01:46:29.417
NHAT HA? IT'S HAI LINH. CAN I CALL YOU?

2085
01:46:29.500 --> 01:46:30.667
<i>Is this Nhat Ha?</i>

2086
01:46:31.250 --> 01:46:32.458
I'm Hai Linh.

2087
01:46:32.542 --> 01:46:33.958
<i>Can we talk for a bit?</i>

2088
01:46:34.042 --> 01:46:35.250
Yes.

2089
01:46:35.833 --> 01:46:39.125
<i>- Then please help me.
- Sure. I'll see you tomorrow.</i>

2090
01:46:41.667 --> 01:46:43.500
<i>Linh. he's calling me.</i>

2091
01:46:44.083 --> 01:46:46.333
<i>Don't tell him I called. Answer him.</i>

2092
01:46:46.417 --> 01:46:48.625
- <i>Bunnie…</i>
- So you finally decided to call me?

2093
01:46:48.708 --> 01:46:50.667
<i>If there's anything you want to ask.
go ahead.</i>

2094
01:46:50.750 --> 01:46:52.667
<i>I won't run away anymore.</i>

2095
01:46:52.750 --> 01:46:54.167
I'll give you 40 grand.

2096
01:46:54.250 --> 01:46:55.875
If that's your offer. then fine.

2097
01:46:55.958 --> 01:46:57.268
Just give me the money
and be done with it.

2098
01:46:57.292 --> 01:46:58.684
-JUST ACCEPT WHATEVER HE WANTS.
-OKAY

2099
01:46:58.708 --> 01:46:59.792
<i>I'm truly sorry.</i>

2100
01:47:01.000 --> 01:47:02.667
<i>Thank you for understanding me.</i>

2101
01:47:03.292 --> 01:47:04.292
Good morning.

2102
01:47:25.750 --> 01:47:27.667
Is there anything else you want to ask?

2103
01:47:28.458 --> 01:47:29.625
That's enough.

2104
01:47:35.250 --> 01:47:36.625
Why are you such a coward?

2105
01:47:39.458 --> 01:47:40.667
You chose to cheat.

2106
01:47:41.208 --> 01:47:43.375
then at least
you should've had more balls.

2107
01:47:44.833 --> 01:47:47.917
Why did you choose to turn me
into the villain in your story?

2108
01:47:51.792 --> 01:47:53.292
I'm sorry.

2109
01:47:53.375 --> 01:47:55.958
But I swear to you. I never once intended

2110
01:47:56.042 --> 01:47:58.917
to destroy anyone's family happiness.

2111
01:47:59.458 --> 01:48:01.333
<i>You know. I was in a relationship too.</i>

2112
01:48:01.417 --> 01:48:02.958
<i>and I wasn't happy either.</i>

2113
01:48:03.500 --> 01:48:06.083
The way he talked to me about you

2114
01:48:06.167 --> 01:48:09.333
<i>made me feel like
you were hurting him too.</i>

2115
01:48:09.417 --> 01:48:11.625
- Feeling better now?
- A little.

2116
01:48:12.208 --> 01:48:13.976
Talking to a happy person
really is different.

2117
01:48:14.000 --> 01:48:16.500
Honestly. I'm not
much better off than you.

2118
01:48:17.125 --> 01:48:19.208
<i>I think we're the same.</i>

2119
01:48:19.292 --> 01:48:21.750
If I told you I wasn't happy right now.
would you believe me?

2120
01:48:21.833 --> 01:48:24.958
This marriage feels like part of her job.

2121
01:48:25.042 --> 01:48:26.667
She's obsessed with right and wrong.

2122
01:48:26.750 --> 01:48:29.917
But somehow. she's always right.
and I'm always wrong.

2123
01:48:31.333 --> 01:48:33.458
<i>Why are we both so miserable?</i>

2124
01:48:33.542 --> 01:48:35.000
If I had known from the beginning

2125
01:48:35.083 --> 01:48:36.750
that your relationship was like this.

2126
01:48:36.833 --> 01:48:39.833
I would never have gotten
involved with him.

2127
01:48:39.917 --> 01:48:41.000
You're not the other woman.

2128
01:48:41.083 --> 01:48:42.351
We've been separated for a while.

2129
01:48:42.375 --> 01:48:43.958
Just waiting on the divorce paperwork.

2130
01:48:44.708 --> 01:48:46.208
He loved you terribly.

2131
01:48:46.833 --> 01:48:48.042
<i>Let me try. okay?</i>

2132
01:48:49.542 --> 01:48:52.125
<i>If I were you.
I'd probably fall for it too.</i>

2133
01:48:52.792 --> 01:48:54.032
<i>You were drowning in the ocean.</i>

2134
01:48:54.083 --> 01:48:56.000
<i>and someone threw you a life ring.</i>

2135
01:48:56.083 --> 01:48:57.792
<i>promising to pull you back to shore.</i>

2136
01:48:57.875 --> 01:48:59.333
<i>Of course you grabbed it.</i>

2137
01:49:00.250 --> 01:49:01.583
<i>I don't blame you.</i>

2138
01:49:02.167 --> 01:49:04.083
My husband is such a good screenwriter.

2139
01:49:06.042 --> 01:49:08.083
If from the very beginning
you had come to me

2140
01:49:08.167 --> 01:49:10.208
and said you liked me.

2141
01:49:10.292 --> 01:49:12.500
but you only wanted me at that moment.

2142
01:49:12.583 --> 01:49:14.917
that this was just a game. pay-to-play.

2143
01:49:15.000 --> 01:49:17.333
then any girl who lied to you
or wanted your money

2144
01:49:17.417 --> 01:49:18.958
would've come willingly.

2145
01:49:19.042 --> 01:49:20.882
But instead. you made me
fall in love with you.

2146
01:49:21.458 --> 01:49:23.042
<i>You painted a future for me.</i>

2147
01:49:23.125 --> 01:49:27.083
<i>You gave me hope
that you'd leave your wife and be with me.</i>

2148
01:49:27.167 --> 01:49:30.500
<i>You made me slowly die in that love.</i>

2149
01:49:31.083 --> 01:49:33.458
When will you and your wife
finally settle things?

2150
01:49:33.542 --> 01:49:35.042
Give me more time.

2151
01:49:35.750 --> 01:49:38.083
I know I promised I'd divorce my wife.

2152
01:49:38.167 --> 01:49:39.917
but it's not as easy as I thought.

2153
01:49:40.000 --> 01:49:41.500
I know you have your own struggles.

2154
01:49:41.583 --> 01:49:43.583
I just need you to say you love me.

2155
01:49:43.667 --> 01:49:46.000
- I can wait for you.
- No. Bunnie...

2156
01:49:46.083 --> 01:49:49.042
- Promise me.
- I can't promise you anything right now.

2157
01:49:49.125 --> 01:49:52.458
You promised you'd divorce Linh
and come to me. Phong.

2158
01:49:53.000 --> 01:49:54.958
What? You don't dare admit it?

2159
01:49:55.583 --> 01:49:59.167
The cruelest thing is giving someone
a hope that isn't real.

2160
01:50:00.875 --> 01:50:03.875
I'm sorry for everything I've caused you.

2161
01:50:03.958 --> 01:50:06.708
And thank you for today.
for helping me let it all out.

2162
01:50:07.375 --> 01:50:09.583
I think after today.
I'll finally be happy.

2163
01:50:09.667 --> 01:50:13.625
So I can be confident
that I've truly forgotten this person.

2164
01:50:15.250 --> 01:50:16.417
This is yours.

2165
01:50:16.500 --> 01:50:19.833
Give me a day or two.
I'll arrange to move out of the apartment.

2166
01:50:22.917 --> 01:50:24.458
I'll get going now.

2167
01:50:31.417 --> 01:50:32.458
Who are you looking for?

2168
01:50:34.333 --> 01:50:36.417
Is this Linh and Phong's house?

2169
01:50:36.500 --> 01:50:38.917
Yes. What's the matter?

2170
01:50:39.000 --> 01:50:40.458
- Are they home?
- Yes.

2171
01:50:41.042 --> 01:50:42.250
Wait here. I'll go call them.

2172
01:50:51.458 --> 01:50:52.458
I'm sorry.

2173
01:51:11.292 --> 01:51:13.500
Guys! Kim's here!

2174
01:51:13.583 --> 01:51:15.542
Can you lock the door? He has a knife!

2175
01:51:16.042 --> 01:51:17.875
- Huh? Who is it?
- Kim! Kim!

2176
01:51:18.875 --> 01:51:19.875
Where's Huong?

2177
01:51:19.917 --> 01:51:21.601
- Are you crazy?
- The other door. the other door!

2178
01:51:21.625 --> 01:51:22.875
Kim!

2179
01:51:22.958 --> 01:51:24.625
Kim. listen to me. Calm down!

2180
01:51:24.708 --> 01:51:26.875
The kitchen door. the kitchen door!

2181
01:51:28.542 --> 01:51:30.583
Kim! Kim! Kim!

2182
01:51:30.667 --> 01:51:31.667
Fuck!

2183
01:51:31.750 --> 01:51:34.042
Listen to me! Calm down. Kim!
Put the knife down.

2184
01:51:34.125 --> 01:51:35.458
Don't do this anymore!

2185
01:51:35.542 --> 01:51:37.292
Kim. can you please stop acting like this?

2186
01:51:37.375 --> 01:51:38.375
Run!

2187
01:51:38.417 --> 01:51:40.542
- Run. Phong!
- Go hide in the basement!

2188
01:51:40.625 --> 01:51:42.583
- Run! Run!
- Call the police right away!

2189
01:51:42.667 --> 01:51:43.958
Run! Stop talking!

2190
01:51:44.792 --> 01:51:46.000
Kim! Kim!

2191
01:51:47.917 --> 01:51:49.208
We've gotta find cover now!

2192
01:51:49.292 --> 01:51:51.083
We've gotta call for help.

2193
01:51:53.875 --> 01:51:55.125
Kim!

2194
01:51:56.042 --> 01:51:58.458
Calm down! We can talk this out! Kim!

2195
01:51:59.167 --> 01:52:00.583
Kim!

2196
01:52:00.667 --> 01:52:02.208
Calm down! Kim!

2197
01:52:04.208 --> 01:52:05.625
Kim!

2198
01:52:10.500 --> 01:52:11.667
Stay calm. Calm down.

2199
01:52:12.417 --> 01:52:13.833
Please calm down!

2200
01:52:13.917 --> 01:52:15.643
How much money do you want?
I'll give you everything!

2201
01:52:15.667 --> 01:52:16.750
I'm begging you. Kim! Kim!

2202
01:52:16.833 --> 01:52:18.167
Please calm down. Kim!

2203
01:52:18.250 --> 01:52:20.833
Let's talk. Let's negotiate.
I'm begging you. Kim!

2204
01:52:20.917 --> 01:52:22.726
You took everything from me.
and now you want to negotiate?!

2205
01:52:22.750 --> 01:52:25.042
- I'm begging you...
- You wanna negotiate?

2206
01:52:26.083 --> 01:52:27.333
Negotiate?

2207
01:52:33.625 --> 01:52:35.208
You're so fucking rich.

2208
01:52:36.292 --> 01:52:37.833
Your wife is beautiful.

2209
01:52:37.917 --> 01:52:39.250
What the hell more do you want?

2210
01:52:53.792 --> 01:52:54.917
Kim! Kim!

2211
01:52:55.000 --> 01:52:56.167
Don't…

2212
01:53:03.167 --> 01:53:04.708
I don't want to die. Kim…

2213
01:53:04.792 --> 01:53:06.042
I don't want to...

2214
01:53:27.500 --> 01:53:28.667
Don't worry.

2215
01:53:29.417 --> 01:53:30.977
I'm sending your wife down to join you.

2216
01:53:31.625 --> 01:53:33.042
Go explain it to her down there.

2217
01:53:33.125 --> 01:53:34.208
Okay?

2218
01:53:45.917 --> 01:53:47.083
Linh!

2219
01:53:48.125 --> 01:53:49.708
Shoulder Sister!

2220
01:53:51.625 --> 01:53:53.167
Come up here with your husband.

2221
01:53:54.417 --> 01:53:56.083
Come see what I did to him!

2222
01:54:04.458 --> 01:54:07.476
You people are so rich. so comfortable.
and you still go looking for trouble!

2223
01:54:07.500 --> 01:54:10.458
Have you lived your life right
to be telling people to break up?

2224
01:54:10.542 --> 01:54:11.583
Huh?!

2225
01:54:12.500 --> 01:54:13.500
Fuck!

2226
01:54:25.708 --> 01:54:27.958
You've pushed me past my limit. Linh!

2227
01:54:35.458 --> 01:54:36.917
You're here. aren't you?!

2228
01:55:04.458 --> 01:55:05.500
Fuck!

2229
01:55:33.667 --> 01:55:34.792
Fuck you!

2230
01:55:34.875 --> 01:55:35.875
Where are you?

2231
01:55:38.875 --> 01:55:40.125
Linh!

2232
01:55:52.500 --> 01:55:54.292
Let go of her!

2233
01:55:58.583 --> 01:55:59.875
Ha!

2234
01:56:05.458 --> 01:56:06.708
Phong!

2235
01:56:10.042 --> 01:56:11.042
I got you!

2236
01:56:11.125 --> 01:56:12.792
- I got you!
- Please calm down!

2237
01:56:16.542 --> 01:56:17.625
Phong!

2238
01:56:18.792 --> 01:56:21.667
I think you should stop giving out advice.

2239
01:56:21.750 --> 01:56:23.958
Have you lived your life right
to be lecturing others?!

2240
01:56:26.500 --> 01:56:28.042
Let Linh go!

2241
01:56:28.625 --> 01:56:30.292
Do you want me to die?!

2242
01:56:30.958 --> 01:56:33.583
You've lost your mind!
How could you kill people?!

2243
01:56:35.708 --> 01:56:37.667
Listen to me. Put the knife down.

2244
01:56:38.875 --> 01:56:40.167
Give it to me.

2245
01:56:40.250 --> 01:56:41.500
Give it to me!

2246
01:56:42.250 --> 01:56:43.417
Give it!

2247
01:56:51.083 --> 01:56:52.143
It hurts. It hurts so much!

2248
01:56:52.167 --> 01:56:53.458
Okay. hold on.

2249
01:56:53.542 --> 01:56:54.875
Hold on…

2250
01:56:54.958 --> 01:56:56.292
It hurts. It hurts.

2251
01:57:01.500 --> 01:57:03.500
- Kim. I'm sorry…
- Help me… Help me…

2252
01:57:07.125 --> 01:57:07.958
Run!

2253
01:57:08.042 --> 01:57:10.875
Linh. can you go upstairs
and call an ambulance for him?

2254
01:57:10.958 --> 01:57:13.583
Call anything. please. Just go upstairs!

2255
01:57:13.667 --> 01:57:14.750
Phong!

2256
01:57:14.833 --> 01:57:16.125
Bunnie! Bunnie! Bunnie!

2257
01:57:16.208 --> 01:57:17.875
Kim. I'm sorry. I didn't mean to!

2258
01:57:17.958 --> 01:57:19.208
It hurts so bad… It hurts…

2259
01:57:20.208 --> 01:57:22.167
Bunnie! Bunnie! Bunnie!

2260
01:57:23.375 --> 01:57:25.833
- Bunnie…
- Kim. I…

2261
01:57:25.917 --> 01:57:27.500
I told Linh to call an ambulance.

2262
01:57:27.583 --> 01:57:30.833
- We'll go to the hospital. You'll be okay.
- I think I'm dying.

2263
01:57:30.917 --> 01:57:32.208
Listen to me.

2264
01:57:32.292 --> 01:57:33.667
I…

2265
01:57:33.750 --> 01:57:34.917
I…

2266
01:57:35.417 --> 01:57:36.833
I love you so much…

2267
01:57:36.917 --> 01:57:38.833
I'm sorry… I'm so sorry…

2268
01:57:38.917 --> 01:57:40.792
You're crazy! You're not dying…

2269
01:57:40.875 --> 01:57:42.083
I know I am…

2270
01:57:42.583 --> 01:57:44.583
You… try to

2271
01:57:44.667 --> 01:57:45.875
live well. okay?

2272
01:57:45.958 --> 01:57:47.375
Can I kiss you once?

2273
01:57:47.958 --> 01:57:50.083
- Let me kiss you.
- You've lost your mind!

2274
01:57:51.083 --> 01:57:53.583
Kim! Stop messing with my head!

2275
01:57:53.667 --> 01:57:54.792
Try to live well.

2276
01:58:04.833 --> 01:58:06.042
Linh!

2277
01:58:06.125 --> 01:58:08.167
Call an ambulance now!

2278
01:58:10.583 --> 01:58:11.667
Kim!

2279
01:58:44.000 --> 01:58:47.042
Phong! Phong! Look at me. Phong!

2280
01:58:59.583 --> 01:59:02.125
I'm not mad at you anymore. Phong!

2281
01:59:02.208 --> 01:59:05.833
I'm really not mad anymore! Okay. Phong?

2282
01:59:10.458 --> 01:59:13.375
I'm sorry. Phong.
I'm not mad at you anymore.

2283
01:59:23.000 --> 01:59:24.708
You're an idiot. Kim.

2284
01:59:42.542 --> 01:59:44.417
<i>A serious break-in has just occurred</i>

2285
01:59:44.500 --> 01:59:46.375
<i>at the home of MC Hai Linh.</i>

2286
01:59:46.458 --> 01:59:48.417
<i>She was attacked by an unknown suspect.</i>

2287
01:59:48.500 --> 01:59:51.250
<i>Investigators say the suspect acted alone.</i>

2288
01:59:51.333 --> 01:59:53.292
<i>with signs pointing
to a personal conflict.</i>

2289
01:59:53.375 --> 01:59:55.750
<i>and took his own life after the attack.</i>

2290
01:59:55.833 --> 01:59:58.375
<i>Police are urgently clarifying the motive.</i>

2291
01:59:58.458 --> 02:00:01.333
<i>Hai Linh has declined
to comment further on the incident.</i>

2292
02:00:01.417 --> 02:00:07.333
MONTHS LATER

2293
02:00:08.792 --> 02:00:13.000
SHOULDER SISTER

2294
02:00:16.833 --> 02:00:19.208
<i>I just lost someone I cared deeply about.</i>

2295
02:00:20.583 --> 02:00:22.708
So I want to pause everything for now.

2296
02:00:23.500 --> 02:00:26.500
take some time to rest. and reset my life.

2297
02:00:28.000 --> 02:00:30.625
Today will be the final episode
of <i>Shoulder Sister</i>.

2298
02:00:31.625 --> 02:00:33.833
- What's wrong with her?
- The show's good though.

2299
02:00:33.917 --> 02:00:36.500
I have given everyone
so much advice already.

2300
02:00:37.208 --> 02:00:40.292
And this is the last piece of advice
I want to give all of you.

2301
02:00:40.375 --> 02:00:42.000
That is…

2302
02:00:43.083 --> 02:00:45.000
Don't rush to follow anyone's advice.

2303
02:00:45.833 --> 02:00:47.833
No one understands you better than you do.

2304
02:00:48.417 --> 02:00:49.917
<i>So…</i>

2305
02:00:50.000 --> 02:00:52.125
<i>Go ahead and experience things
for yourselves.</i>

2306
02:00:56.583 --> 02:00:57.917
<i>All the biggest mistakes</i>

2307
02:00:58.000 --> 02:01:01.292
<i>come from actions
that seem harmless at first.</i>

2308
02:01:01.875 --> 02:01:03.708
<i>Everyone makes mistakes.</i>

2309
02:01:03.792 --> 02:01:05.583
<i>but very few realize they were wrong.</i>

2310
02:01:07.333 --> 02:01:09.375
<i>Some mistakes can never be fixed.</i>

2311
02:01:09.958 --> 02:01:11.708
<i>Only awareness.</i>

2312
02:01:11.792 --> 02:01:15.250
<i>time. and forgiveness can ease the pain.</i>

2313
02:01:16.917 --> 02:01:19.333
<i>And I realized that. in the end.
I was just a child</i>

2314
02:01:19.417 --> 02:01:21.583
<i>desperately craving love.</i>

2315
02:01:21.667 --> 02:01:23.667
<i>but not knowing how to love.</i>

2316
02:01:25.000 --> 02:01:27.292
So through my story. I want to…

2317
02:01:28.417 --> 02:01:30.333
Tell everyone to…

2318
02:01:30.417 --> 02:01:32.458
Remember to cherish the people around you.

2319
02:01:33.208 --> 02:01:34.333
people right beside you.

2320
02:01:35.250 --> 02:01:37.208
Because these are often the people…

2321
02:01:37.750 --> 02:01:39.500
We forget are important.

2322
02:01:41.167 --> 02:01:42.417
Thank you. everyone.

2323
02:01:43.167 --> 02:01:44.917
Linh. we all love you!

2324
02:01:45.000 --> 02:01:46.208
Goodbye. everyone.

2325
02:01:46.750 --> 02:01:48.167
Goodbye. Shoulder Sister.

2326
02:01:48.250 --> 02:01:50.417
Ten out of ten. Hai Linh! I love you!

2327
02:01:50.500 --> 02:01:52.167
Amazing. Hai Linh!

2328
02:01:52.250 --> 02:01:54.083
Linh. I love you!

2329
02:02:26.625 --> 02:02:29.417
<i>In the past.
I rarely felt empathy for other people.</i>

2330
02:02:30.792 --> 02:02:33.042
<i>I thought everything could be solved.</i>

2331
02:02:33.125 --> 02:02:35.292
<i>Why did people make things seem so hard?</i>

2332
02:02:36.167 --> 02:02:37.750
<i>But after everything.</i>

2333
02:02:37.833 --> 02:02:41.958
<i>I realized I had never really put myself
in their shoes to understand them.</i>

2334
02:02:44.500 --> 02:02:48.875
<i>These people used to feel.
to me. loud and annoying.</i>

2335
02:02:50.875 --> 02:02:52.833
<i>So why do they feel so lovable now?</i>

2336
02:03:06.708 --> 02:03:09.292
<i>I'm someone who always tries hard in life.</i>

2337
02:03:10.250 --> 02:03:12.083
<i>but probably only at work.</i>

2338
02:03:12.875 --> 02:03:15.625
<i>not hard enough to truly learn
how to love someone.</i>

2339
02:03:18.958 --> 02:03:21.083
<i>If there were a miracle.
if I could go back.</i>

2340
02:03:21.167 --> 02:03:23.958
<i>I think I would listen to him
and understand him more.</i>

2341
02:03:25.083 --> 02:03:26.167
<i>Because I know that.</i>

2342
02:03:26.250 --> 02:03:28.042
<i>deep down.</i>

2343
02:03:28.125 --> 02:03:31.125
<i>Phong loved me and never meant to hurt me.</i>

2344
02:03:31.875 --> 02:03:32.958
Do you love me?

2345
02:03:34.542 --> 02:03:35.792
I'll love you 'til I die.

2346
02:03:39.125 --> 02:03:40.375
<i>Phong!</i>

2347
02:03:43.542 --> 02:03:45.292
<i>Let's forgive each other.</i>

2348
02:03:46.305 --> 02:04:46.948
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
